Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:33.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,片名：血色将至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:17.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,1898年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,找到她了，找到她了…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}There she is. There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,终于找到了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,新墨西哥，恩格尔   - 渣化试金银法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:16.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,1902年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:39.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,我穿越了半个州，今晚来到这里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I've traveled over half our state to be here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,我本该早些过来，但由于   我在野狼山的新油井刚开始出油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I couldn't get away sooner because my new well was coming in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:44.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,有些事要安排，一时间脱不开身\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   at Coyote Hills and I had to see about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:48.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,那口井现在的出油量是两千桶…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   That well is now flowing at 2,000 barrels
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:51.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,每周都能给我带来五千美金收入\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   and it's paying me an income of $5,000 a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:55.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,我在别处还有两支勘探队   在羚羊谷有十六口产油井\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have two others drilling and I have 16 producing at Antelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:59.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,所以说，如果我自称是一名油矿主   你们应该不会反对\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}so, ladies and gentlemen, if I say I'm an oilman, you will agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们现在面对的机会绝佳…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, you have a great chance here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,但别忘了，如果疏忽大意   到头来可能会一无所获\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}but bear in mind you could lose it all if you're not careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,也许有很多人在想租你们的地，钻井探油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Out of all men that beg for a chance to drill your lots,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,但20个人里面，可能只有一个是油矿主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}maybe one in twenty will be oilmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,其余的家伙都是些投机分子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The rest will be speculators,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:18.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,他们只想当矿主租地生意的中介人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}that's men trying to get between you and the oilmen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,将应属于你们的部分财富攫为己有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}to get some of the money that ought, by rights, come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,即便你们找到个有钱又肯钻井的主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Even if you find one that has money and means to drill,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,多半是个对钻探一无所知的门外汉\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}he'll maybe know nothing about drilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,这种人通常会把项目转托给承包商\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He'll have to hire the job out on contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们的命运也押在了承包商手上…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and then you're depending on a contractor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,而承包商往往应付一下就早早收工\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}who'll rush the job through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,用省出的时间换新的一份承包合同\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}so he can get another contract just as quick as he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们这一行的规则就是如此\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is the way that this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 那你肯给我们多少？   - 我们在浪费时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What is your offer? We're wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,请安静！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,我亲自负责钻探…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I do my own drilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:51.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,凡是为我工作的，只有我一个老板   每个工人我都了如指掌\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And the men that work for me, work for me, and they are men I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:55.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会把办公室搬到钻探现场   实地视察手下的工作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I make it my business to be there and to see their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的人不会笨到把工具掉到井里   然后再花几个月在摸找工具上面\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't lose my tools in the hole and spend months fishing for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,也不会愚蠢地凿穿固井层\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't botch the cementing off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,白白让渗水毁了整口油井\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and let water in the hole and ruin the whole lease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个家庭观念很重的男人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm a family man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:10.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,把钻井开油当成家族产业在做   这是我的儿子兼合伙人H.W. 普莱维\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I run a family business. This is my son and my partner, H.W. Plainview.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:16.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们的理念是，大伙在一起就是一家人   虽然很少有油矿主能认同这种理念\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We offer you the bond of family that very few oilmen can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:21.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,有一点我与其他同行都不一样   我打算在此处扎根，长期采油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm fixed like no other company in this field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,因为我的野狼山油井已开始出油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and that's because my Coyote Hills well has just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,我拥有成套的钻探工具   可随时投入工作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have a string of tools all ready to put to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,我在别处的钻井设备可立即装车   一周内就能运达这里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I can load a rig onto trucks and have them here in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,我有许多贸易伙伴   能搞到搭建井架的木料\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have business connections, so I can get the lumber for the derricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:36.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,只有靠朋友办事才会有这种速度\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Such things go by friendship in a rush like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:40.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,所以我才敢在这儿和你们拍板   不仅可以立即开工\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And this is why I can guarantee to start drilling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,还能拿出充足的资金   以证明我所言非虚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and to put up the cash to back my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们，我向你们保证\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I assure you, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,其他人不管说得如何天花乱坠\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}no matter what the others promise to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:52.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,当万事俱备，只等开工的时候   他们就一个个地不见人影了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}when it comes to the showdown, they won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,坐下！坐下，你不能…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Sit down! Sit down, you have no right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,让我们谈谈最重要的话题\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let us discuss what the man has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:02.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 普雷斯科特，你相信他么？   - 让我们谈谈最重要的话题\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let us discuss what the man has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,- Prescott, do you trust this man? - Let's discuss what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:06.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 他说的在理   - 他怎么知道？那是我的地！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- There's logic to what he's saying. - How does he know? My lot is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:11.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,他说两到三年，也许是十年！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Two or three years, it could be ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 到头来一场空！   - 可他刚开了一口油井！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We gain nothing by losing our heads! - Look at that well out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,没人会一场空\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Nobody's losing their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,你在这儿又没生意！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You have no business being here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,让那个女的坐好，先生！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Sit that woman down, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,你坐下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You can sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,普莱维先生！请留步，普莱维先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Plainview! Please, Mr. Plainview.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,不，普莱维先生，你要去哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No, Mr. Plainview! No, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 谢你好意，但我不想签约了   - 但我们需要你！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I don't need the lease. Thank you. - But we need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,不同的意见太多了   耽误你时间了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Too much confusion. Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,不不不，我们没有不同意见\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No, no, there's no confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:43.08,zimu,,0,0,0,,即使现在把开采权白送给我   我也不会在租约上签字的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I wouldn't take the lease if you gave it to me as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,班克塞先生，我不想浪费您的时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Mr. Bankside, I'm not going to waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,希望您也别浪费我的时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I'd certainly appreciate it if you didn't waste mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:03.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果与我签了合同   十天内就可以开始钻井\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, if you wish to sign with me, we can have a well drilling within 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:07.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,您的土地位于出油点的北面较远处\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Your lot is further north from the discovery well up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,这意味着可能要挖得更深才能见油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That means we'll probably have to dig deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果不出在下所料…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And if there's as much oil here as I think there is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,在您那儿找油会更加困难一些   但只要找到油，开采不成问题\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}it'll be harder to reach, but once we find it, we can take it right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:20.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们必须得加快行动，否则过不多久   这片地区的石油就会被开采殆尽的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have to act quickly, because very soon these fields will be dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,希望你们快做决定\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I need you to know what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,由于距离石油发现点较远…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, because of the distance from the discovery well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的收益分成将比预计的少一些\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll pay you a smaller royalty than you'd get down there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:32.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我愿多付您一千美元作征地补偿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}but I'm prepared to give you a $1,000 bonus on your lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,你说的收益分成是多少？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What kind of royalty are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:38.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,六分之一，外加十天内开工保证\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}One-sixth, plus a guarantee to start drilling within 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,没有比这更公道的价钱了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, that's something you won't find anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,夫人，你的孩子几岁了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What age are your children, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,一个十岁，另一个十二\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ten and twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:59.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,我有个问题，普莱维先生   您的夫人呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Plainview, a question, sir. Where is your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:04.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,班克赛夫人，她死于难产\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}She died in childbirth, Mrs. Bankside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在只剩我们父子两个了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So it's just me and my son now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,老板，出油了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's coming in, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,听这声音！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,普莱维先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Plainview?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,哪位？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,您就是丹尼尔·普莱维？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Are you Daniel Plainview?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,能为你效劳么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,您在找石油？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You look for oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:08.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果一个地方有油   您愿为此付多少钱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What do you pay for a place that has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 要看情况了   - 看哪些情况？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Well, that depends. - What does it depend on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,有许多因素\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}On a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:21.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果我知道哪块地方有油   而且那儿的地价又很便宜\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If I told you I knew a place that had oil where land could be bought cheaply,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:24.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,您认为这个情报值多少钱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}what do you think that would be worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:29.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,你得让我先了解你都知道些什么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I think that you should let me know what you know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:32.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后我们再慢慢谈\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and then we'll try and work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我能坐下么？   - 请坐吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Can I sit down? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,请问您是哪个教派的？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What church do you belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.24,zimu,,0,0,0,,我么…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,各种信仰我都不排斥…   也没有特别确定的教派\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I enjoy all faiths. I don't belong to one church in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:07.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,所有教派我都喜欢…我热爱一切   你从哪儿来？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I like them all. I like everything. Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:11.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,我一会儿告诉你   这也是我要卖给你的情报\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That would be telling you. That's what I want to sell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:16.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,你在信号山这儿干什么工作？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What are you doing in Signal Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们那儿的油，多得都渗出地面了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have oil, and it seeps through the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,想知道在哪儿么？付点钱给我吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you want to pay me to know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,光是地表冒油…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just 'cause there's something on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,并不代表地底下有油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}doesn't mean there's anything beneath it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:26.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,那为何标准石油公司要在我们那儿   大肆收购土地？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Why did Standard Oil buy up land?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,你说的地方在加利福尼亚？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is it in California?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:34.71,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 也许在   - 他们买下了多少土地？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Maybe. - How much land did they buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:38.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,希望你不是在怀疑我的智商   那样我会好受一点\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like it better if you didn't think I was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:49.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,你为什么来找我？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Why did you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:53.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 因为你在这儿的油井出油了   - 说的也是\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- You just brought this well in. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:57.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,好吧，要不这样， 你给我500元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, so just give me $500 in cash right now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,我就把我知道的地方告诉你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I'll tell you where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,年轻人，我的想法是这样的   我先给你100元…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll tell you what I'll do, son. I'll give you $100 now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:07.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果那块地方真的有利可图   我再奖给你1000元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and if it proves to be a promising lease, then give you a $1,000 bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:09.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,先给我600元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Six hundred dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:15.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,为了帮助判断，告诉我一件事情   你们那儿有些什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Tell me one thing to help me decide. What else have you got up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:17.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,种着什么作物？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What do you grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:20.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,是一片大牧场，但大部分都是石地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have a big ranch, but it's mostly rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:23.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,除了野草，种什么都没收成\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Plant things. Nothing will grow but weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:24.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,你认为上面能长什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What makes you think it's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,那附近有硫磺或盐碱矿么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is there sulfur around? Or alkali deposits?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,有盐碱矿，硫磺是什么我不清楚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Alkali nearby. I don't know sulfur.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:39.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,那是你儿子？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is that your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:41.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:43.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你好   - 你好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:49.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 请问您是哪位？   - 我叫弗莱彻·哈密尔顿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Who are you? - I'm Fletcher Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:52.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你，年轻人   你叫什么名？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Nice to meet you, son. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:53.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是干什么的？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:56.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,我为普莱维先生工作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I work with Mr. Plainview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:22:59.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是500美金\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Here's $500, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,再说点有用的，这钱就给你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You tell me something worth hearing, this money's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:11.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,我来自伊莎贝拉郡的小波士顿镇\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I come from a town called Little Boston in Isabella County.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:17.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们在这里   这里是小波士顿的马刺火车站\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is us, here. Spur station here at Little Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:20.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们要找的是桑迪农场\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Sunday ranch is what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:23.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们可以顺着这条放羊道走\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}There's a sheep trail that takes you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:26.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,出镇往西走一英里，不是很远的地方\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's a mile out of town headed west, not far.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:30.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,穿过山脚下的这个小小隘口\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just through a small pass here near the base of the hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:34.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,再经过一座教堂   然后顺着放羊道走就到了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You'll pass a church and just follow the sheep trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:38.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 标准石油公司买了哪几块地？   - 这儿，还有这儿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Where's Standard buying up? - Here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:43.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你的家人姓桑迪？   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Your family name is Sunday, yes? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,家里有几口人？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How many's in your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:47.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,我父母，几个姐妹，还有我兄弟伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My father and mother and sisters and my brother Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:50.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你有几个姐妹？   - 两个\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- How many sisters do you have? - Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:53.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么？   - 保罗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What's your name? - Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:56.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,你家人知道那儿附近有石油么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Does any of your family know about the oil that you say is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不清楚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:00.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,我叔叔常说附近有油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My uncle always said there was oil there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我不知道其他人听说过没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}but I don't know what they heard or what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们种些什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What do you grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:10.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,养了些羊，是个放羊的牧场   我说过，那儿除了野草什么都不长\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lt's goats. It's a goat farm. I told you, nothing grows but weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:12.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 有水源么？   - 有，但水质很咸\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Is there water? - It's salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:16.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,打井取水，很少能取到不咸的水\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You drill a well, it's hard not to get saltwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.15,0:24:21.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定，那儿有石油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The oil is there. I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:29.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我要走了，那么……   - 今晚就住这里好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I want to go now, so... - You can stay tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:33.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 不，我想走，我得离开这里   - 听着，保罗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- No, I want to go now. I want to leave. - Listen, Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.46,0:24:40.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,假如我大老远跑到那儿   结果发现你是在说谎…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If I travel all the way out there and I find that you've been lying to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:42.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会抓到你，让你吐出更多的钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going to find you and I'm going to take more than my money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.07,0:24:45.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,你觉得这样可以么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:47.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 可以，先生   - 那就这样吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes, sir. - All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.38,0:24:52.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 祝您好运，愿主保佑你   - 你也一样，年轻人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Nice luck to you. God bless. - And to you, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.95,0:26:33.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 有人过来了   - 谢谢，玛丽\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- There's someone coming. - Thank you, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.69,0:26:47.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 晚上好   - 晚上好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Good evening. - Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.76,0:26:53.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,我叫丹尼尔·普莱维   这是我儿子HW\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My name's Daniel Plainview. This is my son, H.W.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.90,0:26:56.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你们来打猎么？   - 来猎鹌鹑\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Are you hunting? - Hunting for quail.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.77,0:26:59.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,先前听别人说桑迪农场附近   有块地方适合露营\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We're told there might be a good place to camp up near the Sunday ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.74,0:27:01.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿就是桑迪农场   你们可以在这里露营\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is the Sunday ranch. You can camp here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.71,0:27:04.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你，有水么？   - 有的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Thank you. Do you have water? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.41,0:27:07.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,听说这儿几天前发生了地震\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We heard there was an earthquake up here a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.55,0:27:09.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是真的么？   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Is that right? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.25,0:27:13.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你家人好么？   - 他们都好，谢谢关心\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Your family? - Yeah, all fine. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.56,0:27:18.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 如果不介意，我们有羊奶   - 那样也好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We have goat's milk, if you'd like. - That would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:22.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:27.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果我们把帐篷扎在那儿   就不会挡你们的路了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}if we set our tent away over there, we'd be out of your way over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.07,0:27:29.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.44,0:27:31.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,露丝，来帮忙，带点水过来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ruth! Help these men and bring them some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.74,0:27:33.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,不用！H.W你去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No! H.W.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.08,0:27:38.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,普莱维先生，要不要现在来点羊奶？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Plainview, would you like that milk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.68,0:27:42.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 好的，谢谢   - 玛丽，拿点羊奶来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- That would be fine. Thank you. - Mary! Bring them some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.88,0:27:44.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,我家人会帮你扎帐篷的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My family will help you set up your tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.42,0:27:46.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,不用了，谢谢   我们一路上都是自己动手的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No, please. We set ourselves on this camping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.75,0:27:48.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们得自己扎营\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have to do the camping.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.56,0:27:49.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,快点！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.89,0:27:56.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 有面包么   - 只有土豆\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Do you have bread? - We have potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.03,0:27:58.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,土豆也可以，谢谢你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Potatoes would be nice, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.77,0:28:00.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,我让她们去把土豆煮好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll have them boil you up some potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.37,0:28:02.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,没关系，我们可以自己烤\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's all right. I thought maybe we'd make a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.77,0:28:05.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,我准备带儿子一起生堆篝火\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I wanted to work with my son on making a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.11,0:28:07.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,那好，我儿子伊莱会送柴火来的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}All right. My son, Eli, will bring you some wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.17,0:28:09.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢盛情款待   您是桑迪先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you so much for your hospitality, Mr. Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.34,0:28:11.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是的   - 我们不会妨碍你们的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes. - And we'll be out of your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.48,0:28:14.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 只是来打鹌鹑的   - 好的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We're just hunting for quail. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.18,0:28:18.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 很抱歉，面包没有了   - 不，没关系\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'm sorry we don't have any bread. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.45,0:28:21.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,这山头种不了粮食，到处都是石头…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Corn doesn't fill out in the hills here. It's mostly rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.39,0:28:24.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,连块像样的粮食地也没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We don't have room to raise the grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.93,0:28:29.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，年轻的小姐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.22,0:28:56.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,我叫伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My name is Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.19,0:29:00.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,你就是伊莱·桑迪吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, you're Eli Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.16,0:29:02.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,欢迎您来这儿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.27,0:29:07.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,- H.W   - 伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- H.W. - Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.27,0:29:16.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你们来猎鹌鹑？   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- You're hunting quail? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.65,0:29:25.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我们会送晚饭过来的   - 谢谢，太感谢你们了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We will bring dinner. - Thank you. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.23,0:30:48.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,爸爸！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.14,0:30:50.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,爸爸，看我的鞋子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Dad, look at my shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.36,0:31:19.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,这些石油是因为地震才冒出来的   我们走\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's earthquake oil. Set loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.52,0:31:44.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,这么说…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   So...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.43,0:31:47.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,怎么说？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   So?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.50,0:31:49.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,这么说的话…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   So, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.66,0:31:53.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果这底下藏着油，可以把它往海边运\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   If there's anything here, we take it to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.10,0:31:58.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们要做的就是建一条输油管线   终点是韦尼缪港或圣保拉\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What we do is we build a pipeline to Port Hueneme or Santa Paula,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.94,0:32:00.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,总长大约100英里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}it's about 100 miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.57,0:32:04.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后把油卖给联合石油公司   我们要做的就是这些\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and we do a deal with Union Oil. This is what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.01,0:32:07.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,这样就不需要铁路了   也不必在货运上花钱了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Then we don't need the railroads and their shipping costs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.08,0:32:09.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.32,0:32:13.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.49,0:32:16.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 全都明白了？   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- You see that? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.22,0:32:19.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后我们就坐等收钱吧   真金白银滚滚而来…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Then we're making money. We're making the real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.56,0:32:21.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,每个硬币都落入我们的腰包\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What we should be making. Not just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.53,0:32:23.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,无需再把钱浪费在运输上了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Not just throwing it away on shipping costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.03,0:32:26.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,不然的话，就剩不下几个钱了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Otherwise, it's just mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.40,0:32:32.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们要付给他们多少钱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How much are we going to pay them?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:35.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,哪个他们？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.05,0:32:39.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,桑迪一家\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Sunday family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:43.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们不用石油的名义买\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm not going to give them oil prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.85,0:32:48.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们用鹌鹑的名义买\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll give them quail prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.86,0:32:55.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,占用您几分钟时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If we could take a few minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.60,0:32:58.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,有件事情很想和您谈谈\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}there's something I'd very much like to talk with you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.87,0:33:02.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,孩儿他妈，把姑娘们带出去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mother, would you take the girls outside, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.41,0:33:17.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,我喜欢直话直说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I believe in plain speaking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.32,0:33:20.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,您的农场很漂亮   我很喜欢猎鹌鹑\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is a beautiful ranch. I love hunting for quail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.86,0:33:24.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,你知道，我儿子身体不太好   他需要多呼吸新鲜空气\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My boy has been sick, you know. He needs fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.03,0:33:28.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,看过的医生都说   最好让他生活在空气清新的地方\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Doctors all say he needs plentiful fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.10,0:33:31.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.67,0:33:37.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,埃布尔，你认为这块地卖多少钱合适？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}what would you say would be a fair price for this lot, Abel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.77,0:33:41.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你要买下这地方？   - 说得没错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- To buy this place? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.35,0:33:48.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,不急，慢慢想\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Take a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.02,0:33:55.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道该卖多少   - 每英亩六美元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'm sorry. I don't know. - Six dollars an acre.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.86,0:33:59.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,六美元？谢谢你开价，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Six dollars? Thank you, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.43,0:34:03.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,这几年装修农场花了不少钱   大概500美元的样子…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And then with the improvements to the ranch over the years at $500...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.26,0:34:05.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,我愿出3700美元买下这片农场\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like to offer you $3,700 for this ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.93,0:34:08.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 一共3700美元   - 不行\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- That's $3,700. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:11.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,伊莱，这个人是上帝派来的啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Lord has sent this man here, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.84,0:34:13.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的，我也相信是上帝让我来的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, I believe He has.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.47,0:34:17.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我给你们的报价是3700美元   - 究竟是什么让你来这里的，先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- My offer to you is $3,700. - What is it that brought you here, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.75,0:34:20.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,是上苍神意的指引\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Good Lord's guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.51,0:34:21.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 当然，除了神意之外…   - 我们的石油呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Now, of course, within that... - What about our oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.95,0:34:23.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,…我们还得签一份合同\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...we're going to develop a lease.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.92,0:34:28.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么？   - 我们的石油呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What's that? - What about our oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.82,0:34:31.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么石油？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.36,0:34:33.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们这儿有石油，应该值不少钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have oil here. That's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.66,0:34:36.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,你能组织人钻探么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you have someone who can drill for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:38.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你认为这儿有石油？   - 我知道这儿有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Do you think there's oil here? - I know there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.27,0:34:40.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,要钻探石油得花很多钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's very expensive to drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.43,0:34:42.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,把油从地底下取出来是大工程   你之前有没有试过自己开采？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}To get it up and out of the ground. You ever tried that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.70,0:34:44.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 要花多少钱？   - 很多钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- How much is it? - Costly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.87,0:34:47.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,但是，这儿的油埋得很浅\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, our oil sits right up on top of the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.98,0:34:50.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,我相信你看到的是渗油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I believe that's called seepage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:52.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,这并不代表下面藏着石油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Doesn't necessarily mean there's anything underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:54.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 为此你准备出多少钱？   - 我没想过\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What would you give us for it? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.75,0:34:57.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 这事你竟然没想过？   - 是的，没错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Something you don't know. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.99,0:35:02.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,你想要多少，伊莱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What would you like, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.69,0:35:06.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,一万美金\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ten thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.20,0:35:10.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,为了什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.63,0:35:14.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,为了我的教堂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}For my church.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:25.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,说得不错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.78,0:35:30.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是个好理由\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:33.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,好罢…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.49,0:35:38.08,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果我们决定在此开采石油   如果此地真能产油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If we decide to drill for oil and if the well begins to produce,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.19,0:35:39.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会给你的教堂捐5000美元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll give your church a $5,000 signing bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.99,0:35:40.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,一万美元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.06,0:35:43.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,你想去找别人来钻探么？ 伊莱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you want to find someone else that's going to come here and drill, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.66,0:35:46.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,投入资金，还要自己出工出力…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Make the investment and do all the hard work that goes into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.90,0:35:50.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,我大可以找一处别的农场   在那儿安安静静的猎鹌鹑\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I can just as easily hunt for quail on another ranch as I can here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.90,0:35:55.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我也很乐意尽全力支持你的教堂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Though I'll happily be a supporter of your church for as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.64,0:35:57.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,前提是这儿真的有石油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}For the bonus only.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.25,0:36:03.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,假如真有油的话   我倒是有些钻探行当的熟人…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, as it happens, I do have some connections in the drilling business
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.15,0:36:07.71,zimu,,0,0,0,,到时候能帮我们做些采油的事情   你觉得怎么样，埃布尔？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}who might help get us started. How do you feel about this, Abel?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.82,0:36:09.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,我没意见，听伊莱的就行\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes. What Eli says.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.86,0:36:13.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,好吧，那这样，先签几份合同\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, good! Let's draw up some contracts and let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.13,0:36:15.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们一起试试看\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.40,0:36:19.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,感谢你的协助，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Appreciate your help with this, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.54,0:36:32.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 下午好   - 下午好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Good afternoon. - Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.28,0:36:33.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 土地管理局？   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Real estate? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.71,0:36:35.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,我找您有事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, I'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.85,0:36:40.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想找几块地，我刚买了桑迪农场\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm looking for some land. I just bought the Sunday ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.49,0:36:44.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后…呃，能看下地图么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And, well, where's the map?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.09,0:36:47.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,桑迪农场后面的丘陵在哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where are the hills behind the Sunday ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.66,0:36:51.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,在这儿，这块土地属于班迪   一共六百多英亩\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's here. It's the Bandy tract. He has over 600 acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.43,0:36:55.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,班迪，六百…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Bandy, 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.64,0:37:02.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 那这块地方呢？   - A.C·莫德、布罗基特、雷德利克、卡尔…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What about this? - A.C. Maude, Blodget, Redlick, Carr.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.81,0:37:06.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 地价多少？   - 每英亩六美元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What's it held at? - Six dollars an acre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.55,0:37:08.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,六美元…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.98,0:37:10.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:14.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,是贝尔文的地，买下应该没问题   我敢肯定\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's the Belvins, and that could be got, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.22,0:37:18.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿附近的土地都能买到手么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can everything around here be got?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.69,0:37:21.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的，肯定\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.49,0:37:48.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,保罗·桑迪曾是我们的好朋友\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Paul Sunday turned out to be a good friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:51.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.59,0:37:57.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,你快点过来吧   叫弗雷德·英吉利一起来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, you get here just as soon as you can. Bring Fred English.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.97,0:38:00.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,好，就这样\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.07,0:38:02.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，师傅\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you, porter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.41,0:38:08.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,- H.W.，你好么？   - 很好，您呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- H.W., how are you? - Fine, and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.14,0:38:10.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 还不错，你爸呢？   - 他在里面\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Pretty good. Where's your dad? - He's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.14,0:38:11.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们大老远从希格诺山到这儿来…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You fellas are a long way from Signal Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.65,0:38:13.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你好啊，普莱维   - 你好，吉恩\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hello, Plainview. - Hello, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.75,0:38:16.24,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见到你   - 你好查理\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Good to see you. - Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.38,0:38:20.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 这是赶着去哪儿？   - 顺路经过这里，就下来看看\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- On your way somewhere else? - Passing through. Looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.05,0:38:23.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你也在这儿，真奇怪啊   - 是啊，我也觉得奇怪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Funny to see you. - Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.69,0:38:26.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的人又在忙家族产业了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You boys are a regular family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.56,0:38:28.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的人这次迟到了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You boys are a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:32.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你发现了什么？   - 一些有趣的东西\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What did you find? - I found some interesting prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.53,0:38:33.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,听说标准石油在此购地了么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Did you hear Standard bought up?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.90,0:38:36.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 他们现在买的地皮大多在镇子北面   - 我也听人这么说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Mostly in the north, so far. - That's what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.60,0:38:40.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,跟你说，吉恩，如果你也想加入   从镇东面开始吧…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm gonna tell you, Gene, if you're gonna make a play, look east.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.17,0:38:45.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,早晚别人会来，我宁愿那人是你   你脚下的这片土地已名花有主了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd rather it be you than someone else. This mud around here has been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.55,0:38:49.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,身边带着个俏脸蛋   每天的阳光都灿烂啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It must be easy when you have such a cute face to carry around with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.22,0:38:52.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你想夸我儿子英俊？   - 就算我是好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Telling me how handsome my son is? - Well, that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.39,0:38:55.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,真动听，谢谢夸奖   祝你好运，吉恩\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's very nice. Thank you. Good luck, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.69,0:38:58.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 多保重   - 听我的话，去东面看看\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Take care. - Like I said, go east.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.26,0:38:59.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,H.W.\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}H.W.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.39,0:39:03.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果你需要签合同，我愿当你的律师\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll be your lawyer if you need to draw up a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.20,0:39:07.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,以免你上人家的当   你老爸赚的钱也该有你一半\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Make sure you don't get swindled, boy. Get half what your dad's making.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.74,0:39:19.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿怎么样?\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.29,0:39:36.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,那些人在做什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What are those men doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.80,0:39:41.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,他们为我们工作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}They're just guys that are working for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.47,0:39:43.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,他们只是在这儿四处看看\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}They're just looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.97,0:39:48.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们能赚多少钱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How much money can we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.25,0:39:54.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不知道，要看情况了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't know. It depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.82,0:40:00.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,一千美元？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}One thousand dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.76,0:40:12.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,玛丽说如果她不祷告，她爸会揍她\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mary said that her father beats her if she doesn't pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.11,0:40:21.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,玛丽，是那个最小的女儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mary, she's the smaller one?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.21,0:40:25.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.53,0:40:42.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 人都到齐了？   - 基本顺利\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Everyone here? - Very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.83,0:40:43.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,但是…？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.00,0:40:47.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,只有一个人，他名下的地产尚无着落\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}There were a few vacant lots and one holdout.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.50,0:40:49.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 谁？   - 威廉·班迪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Who? - William Bandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.24,0:40:51.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,一共八块地…他什么来头？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...eight. Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.40,0:40:52.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,是个老头，在此定居\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's an old man who homesteaded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.91,0:40:56.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,他和孙子一起住   他有话要和你说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Lives with his grandson. He said he'd like to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.18,0:40:57.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,他来了么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.48,0:41:00.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,没来，他希望你亲自上门拜访\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No, he'd like you to come visit with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.65,0:41:02.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,他想抬价？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's boosting his price.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.48,0:41:06.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,他说想和买地的人谈谈\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He said he'd like to speak with whoever is doing the buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.39,0:41:09.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,那就让他等着吧   下次他自己会来的，我们走\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, let him wait. He'll come around. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.73,0:41:18.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们，先生们…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.67,0:41:21.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们，先生们\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.84,0:41:25.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们今晚能来到这儿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you so much for visiting with us this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:28.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,我穿越了半个州   最后把目光投在这片土地上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, I've traveled across half our state to be here and to see about this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.98,0:41:33.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们中有些可能已经听说了…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Now, I daresay some of you might have heard
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.61,0:41:37.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,某些有关本人计划的无边传闻\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   some of the more extravagant rumors about what my plans are,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.55,0:41:40.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想在此亲自道明事实的真相\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   so I just thought you'd like to hear it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.45,0:41:43.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,大家面对面，没什么神秘的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   This is the face. It's no great mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.19,0:41:50.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们，我是一个油矿主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I'm an oilman, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.03,0:41:54.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,我在本州有许多产业\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I have numerous concerns spread across this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.53,0:41:57.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的油井群每日出产几千桶原油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I have many wells flowing at many thousand barrels per day,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.04,0:42:01.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,因此我自认是一名油矿主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   so I like to think of myself as an oilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.01,0:42:03.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,作为一名油矿主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   As an oilman, I hope that you'll forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.91,0:42:06.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,我这人向来有话直说，请各位见谅\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   just good old-fashioned plain speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.45,0:42:11.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,这个行当对我来说，是家族产业\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Now, this work that we do is very much a family enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.12,0:42:14.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的好儿子H.W和我并肩作战\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I work side by side with my wonderful son, H. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.89,0:42:18.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们中有些人可能见过他\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I think one or two of you might have met him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.22,0:42:21.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,我还鼓励手下也将家人带在身边\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   And I encourage my men to bring their families, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.13,0:42:26.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,有家人陪伴，生活也变得更有滋味\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Of course, it makes for an ever so much more rewarding life for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.20,0:42:30.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,成家了就会有孩子   有孩子就该有教育\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Family means children, and children means education.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.30,0:42:33.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,所以不管我们在哪儿落脚   教育都是必不可少的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   So, wherever we set up camp, education is a necessity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.11,0:42:36.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,我也很乐意为孩子提供教育的机会\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   and we're just so happy to take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.44,0:42:38.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要在小波士顿建一流的学校\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So let's build a wonderful school in Little Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.95,0:42:41.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,孩子就是我们为之奋斗的未来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}These children are the future that we strive for,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.28,0:42:44.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,他们理当拥有最好的东西\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and so they should have the very best of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.48,0:42:46.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在，我还要说一件事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.62,0:42:50.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,请恕我冒犯…我要说的是面包\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and please don't be insulted if I speak about this. Bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.59,0:42:52.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,让我们谈谈面包吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let's talk about bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.26,0:42:56.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,我印象中，在这个伟大的国家里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, to my mind, it's an abomination to consider
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.73,0:43:00.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,任何男人，女人或是小孩子   如果把一块面包当作奢侈品\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}that any man, woman, or child in this magnificent country of ours
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.07,0:43:04.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,将是多么的可悲\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}should have to look upon a loaf of bread as a luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.34,0:43:08.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们可在此地挖水井   有了淡水，就能灌溉\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   We're going to dig water wells here, and water wells means irrigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.04,0:43:11.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,有了灌溉，就能种粮食\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Irrigation means cultivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.54,0:43:15.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,那些曾经的不毛之地将变成良田沃野\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   We're going to raise crops here where before it just simply wasn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.55,0:43:17.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,等到收获季节，粮食多得发愁\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   You're going to have more grain than you'll know what to do with,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.08,0:43:21.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,这位女士，你家的面包会堆得淹过脖子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   and bread will be coming right out of your ears, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:26.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,修建道路，发展农业   提供就业，兴办教育…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   New roads, agriculture, employment, education.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.56,0:43:28.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,这只是我们建设计划中的寥寥几项而已\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}These are just a few of the things we can offer you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.63,0:43:30.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们，我向你们保证\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I assure you, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.73,0:43:32.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果在这里找到了石油…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}that if we do find oil here,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.03,0:43:36.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,我觉得此事为真的可能性很大\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I think there's a very good chance that we will,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.57,0:43:41.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们不但能在此地继续繁衍   这片家园还将更加兴旺富强\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}this community of yours will not only survive, it will flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.31,0:43:46.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果有什么问题尽管向我提…   什么问题？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd be happy to answer any questions that you might have. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.45,0:43:48.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,新辟的道路通往教堂么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Will the new road lead to the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.08,0:43:53.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,教堂将会是新路的第一站   谢谢你伊莱，还有问题么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That'll be the first place that it leads. Thank you, Eli. Anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.19,0:43:56.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,那好，如果有其他疑惑   我会一直恭候大驾光临\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, if anything comes up, I'm pretty easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.59,0:43:57.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,到时尽管来找我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You just come visit with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.96,0:43:59.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们今晚的参与，晚安\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you so much for your time, and good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.53,0:44:43.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,“这是我们的特权…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   What a privilege to carry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.64,0:44:47.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,“用祈祷向神祝愿…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   everything to God in prayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.47,0:44:52.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是我们的特权…”\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   What a privilege to carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.40,0:45:11.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,顺着新路走就能到教堂了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just follow the new road right to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.36,0:45:13.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,顺着新路走就不会走错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The new road will lead you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.70,0:45:15.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,你好，兄弟，我叫伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Hello, brother, my name is Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.50,0:45:19.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,第三启示教会欢迎您光临   (第一启示为摩西十诫；第二为耶稣临世   预言中还有第三次末日启示，尚未发生)\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Church of the Third Revelation welcomes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.17,0:45:20.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,你好，兄弟，我叫伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Hello, brother, my name is Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.01,0:45:23.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,第三启示教会欢迎您光临\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Church of the Third Revelation welcomes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.44,0:45:26.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,顺着新路走就能到教堂了.\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just follow the new road right to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.32,0:45:38.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,“耶稣知道世人的罪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Jesus knows our every weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.73,0:45:43.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,“真心祈祷向神忏悔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Take it to the Lord in prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.90,0:45:49.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,“我们脆弱又疲惫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Are we weak and heavy-laden
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.10,0:45:53.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,“他人关切成累赘\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Cumbered with a load of care?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.34,0:45:57.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,“救世主给了我们安慰\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Precious Savior still our refuge
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.48,0:46:02.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,真心祈祷向神忏悔…”\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Take it to the Lord in prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.09,0:46:17.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 能和你说几句么，丹尼尔？   - 可以，请进吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Daniel, may I speak with you? - Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.30,0:46:22.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,等他们到了，我就带过来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll bring them up when they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.40,0:46:24.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 早上好   - 早上好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.74,0:46:26.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,工作进展怎么样？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How is all the work coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.77,0:46:28.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,都很顺利\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Everything's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.31,0:46:31.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 所有工人都已就位？   - 当然\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- All the men are provided for? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.51,0:46:35.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,士气好像很高昂啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Spirits seem high.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.85,0:46:41.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,需要我为你们做什么嘛？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is there anything that you need from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.39,0:46:48.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 需要教会做什么嘛？   - 我想还没有，谢谢你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Anything the church can do for you? - I don't believe so. No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.76,0:46:51.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,听说你让众人明天到这儿集合…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I understand you've asked the people to gather around
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.23,0:46:52.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,一起参加油井开工仪式，有这回事么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and watch the well begin tomorrow. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.93,0:46:54.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 有这么回事   - 我会为油井祈福的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- That's right. - I will bless the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.67,0:46:59.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,在仪式开始前，把我介绍给大家\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Before you begin, you should introduce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.47,0:47:02.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后我会走到油井那里…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You'll see me walk up towards the oil well, and when I...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.14,0:47:03.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,是油井钻架\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The derrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.31,0:47:07.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,…等我走到钻架那儿之后   你就可以介绍我的名字了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You'll see me walk up, and then you could say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.25,0:47:09.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,当你走上来之后…？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}When you walk up?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.48,0:47:13.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的，我会走上来，然后你就说…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes. You'll see me walk up, and then you could say,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.49,0:47:18.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,“他是这片大山的爱子   照料着主的子民…”\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}"The proud son of these hills who tended his Father's flock,"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.86,0:47:21.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后就可以说我的名字了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and then you could say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.56,0:47:24.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.13,0:47:28.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 那之后呢？   - 之后我们就开始钻井\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- And what happens then? - Well, then we start the drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.70,0:47:35.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，虽然祈福仪式很简单   但非常重要\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's a simple blessing, Daniel, but an important one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.47,0:47:38.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,就几句话，不会占用太长时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's just a few words. It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.55,0:47:42.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候开始？   - 你什么时候方便呢，伊莱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What time? - What time's good for you, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.78,0:47:45.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 下午四点   - 那我们就定在四点开始\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- 4:00. - Well, let's make it 4:00 then.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.69,0:47:50.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 感谢你来拜访   - 谢谢您，我走了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- My thanks for your visit. - Good day. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.84,0:48:07.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,各位下午好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Afternoon, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.14,0:48:10.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.15,0:48:19.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,感谢你们每个人来此参加这项仪式\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I thank you all so much for visiting with us at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.75,0:48:21.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,我已有幸拜访过你们中的某些家庭…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've had the pleasure of meeting some of you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.65,0:48:23.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,我也非常希望在今后几个月里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I hope very much in the months to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.62,0:48:26.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,能逐一拜访每户人家\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll be able to visit with each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.93,0:48:29.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,比起钻井找油来   我在演说方面的才能要差许多\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm better at digging holes in the ground than making speeches,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.73,0:48:31.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,所以就不发表长篇大论了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}so let's forget the speech for this evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.40,0:48:33.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,来一段简单的祈福吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}just make it a simple blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.43,0:48:35.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,众所周知，仅凭一个人无法采油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You see, one man doesn't prospect from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.30,0:48:39.24,zimu,,0,0,0,,勘探需要发动群体的力量   在场各位就是合适的人选\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It takes a whole community of good people, such as yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.34,0:48:42.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,只有这样才好，大家住在一起\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and this is good. We stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.44,0:48:44.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,一起祷告，一起工作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We pray together, we work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.31,0:48:47.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,倘若有幸，上帝对我们的努力报以微笑…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and if the Good Lord smiles kindly on our endeavor,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.41,0:48:49.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们还能一起分享天赐的财富\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}we share in the wealth together.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.32,0:48:54.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在，在玛丽一号油井开钻之前…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, before we spud in Mary's Well Number One,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.49,0:48:57.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,借了身边这位可爱小姐   玛丽·桑迪之芳名…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}named for the lovely Miss Mary Sunday, here by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.76,0:49:00.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,她是这片大山的爱女\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}a proud daughter of these hills,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.89,0:49:04.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想说的是: 愿主保佑我们的辛劳\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd just like to say God bless these honest labors of ours, and, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.73,0:49:06.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,愿他也保佑在场的所有子民\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.90,0:49:07.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.10,0:49:09.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在去吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.37,0:49:16.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,马上就好，请稍候\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Won't be a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.21,0:49:21.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,H.W.，给我快点\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Fast as you can, H.W.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.68,0:49:26.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,准备好了没？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Are you ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.66,0:49:39.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们，我们开始了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's it, ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.04,0:49:47.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,感谢阿尔·罗斯的慷慨   大家可以享用些茶点…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Al Rose has very generously provided some refreshments for this occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.24,0:49:49.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,茶点开销由他负责，谢谢你，阿尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}out of his own pocket. Thank you, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.71,0:49:55.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,请尽情享用美食，我马上回来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If you'll all just care to help yourselves, I'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.01,0:51:09.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.21,0:51:12.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,玛丽·桑迪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mary Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.68,0:51:18.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 喜欢你的新裙子么？     - 很喜欢，谢谢您\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Do you like your new dress? - Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.52,0:51:21.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,不客气，我想你会喜欢的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're welcome. I thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.29,0:51:24.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我来这儿你高兴么？     - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Are you happy I came here? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.53,0:51:30.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,你爸爸还打你么？他现在不打你了吧？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Your daddy doesn't hit you anymore, does he? Does he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.10,0:51:32.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,最好他不打了，对么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Better not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.63,0:51:35.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会照顾你的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.74,0:51:41.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,不让他再打你了，好不好？     不许再打了…现在你可以走了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No more hitting, right? No more hitting. Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.01,0:51:45.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,去玩吧，不用过来了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Go and play some more and don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.19,0:51:55.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.29,0:52:03.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,H.W，没什么事，快回去睡觉吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lt's okay, H.W. Go back to sleep. Go on. Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.00,0:52:07.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.57,0:52:10.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.71,0:52:14.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.54,0:52:17.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.84,0:52:19.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.98,0:52:23.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,井下死了个人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Lost a man down the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.62,0:52:29.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 谁？     - 乔伊·冈达\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- What man? - Joe Gundha.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.76,0:52:33.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我认识他么？     - 不\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Did I know him? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.33,0:52:35.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.07,0:52:44.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,往上抬\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.14,0:52:46.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,设好闸\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Set the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.84,0:52:49.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 绑好往下放     - 快绑好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Tie it down. - Tie it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.75,0:52:55.08,zimu,,0,0,0,,该死！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.15,0:52:59.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的天哪，尸体在哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}God damn it. Where's the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.29,0:53:03.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 正在打捞     - 好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- They're fishing it out now. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.66,0:53:09.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 钻头呢？     - 在平台上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Where's the bit? - It's on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.84,0:53:55.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,把尸体弄干净，然后给他换套衣服\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Clean him up. Put some clothes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.81,0:53:58.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.71,0:54:01.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,再支一个帐篷\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Set up a tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.38,0:54:05.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,任何人下井之前，必须告知他人     听见没有？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Anyone goes down into the cellar, you tell somebody. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.98,0:54:07.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 听见了，先生     - 知道了，先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.32,0:54:13.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,先停工，到中午再说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Shut down till midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.66,0:54:50.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,我还做了一个梦     是的，昨夜，我做了个梦\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And I had a vision. Yes, last night, I had a vision
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.16,0:54:53.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,我感觉上帝的气息贯穿全身\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I felt God's breath move through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.70,0:55:00.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,最后来到我的胃中\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And it rolled down into my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.81,0:55:04.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,气息在胃中翻滚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It sloshed around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.08,0:55:09.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的胃开始说话，不是呼喊，而是低语\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And my stomach spoke in a whisper, not a shout,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.19,0:55:17.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 用手触摸这名妇人，轻抚她的肌肤     - 是这样\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}"Touch this woman with your hands and caress her." Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.76,0:55:23.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,亲爱的亨特太太…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My dear Mrs. Hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.10,0:55:27.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,你患有关节炎，是不是？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}you have arthritis, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.57,0:55:29.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是的，伊莱     - 是啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes, I do, Eli. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.67,0:55:33.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,有恶魔藏在你的手中     我要把这魔鬼吸出来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The devil is in your hands, and I will suck it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.44,0:55:38.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,这回我不准备用热焰逼它出来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, I will not cast this ghost out with a fever
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.04,0:55:44.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,我内中的气息，教给我一种新的交流方式\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}for the new spirit inside me has shown me I have a new way to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.55,0:55:48.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,用温柔的低语呼唤\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It is a gentle whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.96,0:55:57.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,出来吧，魔鬼\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of here, ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.90,0:56:02.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,从里面出来吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of here, ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.27,0:56:05.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,出来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.30,0:56:09.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,出来吧，魔鬼\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of here, ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.58,0:56:14.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,从里面出来吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of here, ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.88,0:56:18.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在就离开这个女人，给我出来…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...and enter this woman's body now. - Get out of here, ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.88,0:56:23.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,出来后再也不要停留，永远离开\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of here. Don't you dare turn around and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.92,0:56:26.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果你敢回来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}For if you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.73,0:56:32.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会将愤怒的力量汇于脚尖     踢碎你的利齿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}all the armies of my boot will kick you in the teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.36,0:56:35.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,将你高高抛起，而后摔在泥中\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and you will be cast up and thrown in the dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.00,0:56:38.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,堕入地狱，永不超生！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and thrust back to perdition!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.50,0:56:42.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,只要我有牙齿，就会来撕咬你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And as long as I have teeth, I will bite you,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.34,0:56:46.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果没有牙齿，就用牙床嚼死你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and if I have no teeth, I will gum you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.41,0:56:50.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,只要我有双拳，就要来痛揍你！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And as long as I have fists, I will bash you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.25,0:56:54.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,快点给我离开，魔鬼！     快离开，魔鬼！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, get out of here, ghost! Get out of here, ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.12,0:56:58.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,快离开，魔鬼！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of here, ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.33,0:57:02.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,它走了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And it left!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.70,0:57:05.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 哈利路亚!     - 哈利路亚!\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hallelujah! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.23,0:57:09.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 赞美主，赞美神圣日！     - 赞美主！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Praise the Lord and his holy days! - Praise God!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.80,0:57:13.24,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 阿门！谢谢各位     - 感谢耶稣，感谢主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Amen! Thank you. - Thank you, Jesus. Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.51,0:57:16.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,亲爱的亨特太太\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My dear Mrs. Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.28,0:57:22.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,跟我跳支舞吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Dance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.25,0:57:31.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 感谢光临     - 真是一次美妙的布道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Thanks for coming. - It was a wonderful sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.69,0:57:34.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 明天见？     - 明天见\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Will I see you tomorrow? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.10,0:57:40.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Eli.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.63,0:57:45.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,油井昨晚发生了一场悲剧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Had a tragedy at the well last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.67,0:57:48.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的，我听说了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.47,0:57:50.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,乔伊·冈达是个有虔诚信仰的人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Joe Gundha was a man of considerable faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.98,0:57:55.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,他的葬礼在明天中午     你可以过来讲几句话\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So if you wish to say a few words, his burial is at noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.31,0:57:58.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，事故本来可以避免\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, this accident could have been avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.28,0:58:00.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,在未蒙主恩的井下工作…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It is terrible to think of that well
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.49,0:58:02.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 实在太可怕了…     - 我的人12小时才换一班\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- working away out there... - These men work in 12-hour shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.45,0:58:03.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,他们需要充分的休息\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...unblessed. - They need their rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.59,0:58:05.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果得不到充分休息     他们就会犯低级错误\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If they don't have it, they start to make stupid mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.42,0:58:08.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,我看见有人在工作时酗酒     难道你不应对此采取措施？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've seen the men drinking. Don't you think that has something to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.29,0:58:09.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的人需要充分休息     油井的生产才有保证\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We need these men well-rested to bring in this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.89,0:58:12.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果他们总来听你传道     就无法保证正常的休息\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}They can't get that if they're up here listening to your gospel,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.16,0:58:14.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,那样的话，我们就没法产油     大家的钱也成了泡影\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and then the well can't produce and blow gold all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.43,0:58:16.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,我希望，当初要能多接触乔伊就好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I wish I had more time with Joe Gundha.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.53,0:58:17.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,也许我能帮他更多\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}More could have been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.87,0:58:22.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,那样我们就没法产油     大家的钱也成了泡影\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Then the well can't produce and blow gold all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.21,0:58:31.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,你能否帮个忙，将他的私人财产…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, would you see to it that his personal possessions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.62,0:58:33.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,转交给他的家人，好么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}find their way back to his family, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.89,0:58:35.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.89,0:58:39.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,听说你正计划改建教堂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Heard you were planning some renovations.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.12,0:58:42.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,是啊，聚会人数越来越多\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, our congregation is growing strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.76,0:58:47.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我们需要更大的地方     - 你刚才那场跳神表演真是妙的很啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We need more room. - That was one goddamn hell of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.37,0:58:50.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,很荣幸有你相伴，丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We were happy to have you, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.52,1:00:46.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,瓦斯，瓦斯！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Gas, gas, gas!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.33,1:00:58.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,火源灭了！等在这儿     快灭了火源！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Lights out! Wait here. Wait here. Lights out!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.57,1:01:10.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,快把那火掐了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Put that fire out!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.24,1:01:41.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,他受伤没有？H. W！     把他递给我！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is he hurt? H.W.! Hand him down to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.58,1:01:47.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 把他放下来！     - 接住\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hand him down! - Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.95,1:01:54.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 抓住没？     - 抓住了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Got him? - I've got him!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.36,1:02:02.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,哦，老天\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.14,1:02:19.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,坚持住\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.69,1:02:33.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,把门打开\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.07,1:02:50.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,放开手吧，你没事了，你安全了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let go. There you go. You're safe. You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.78,1:02:55.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,你现在安全了，我把你带回来了     你安全了，把手放开吧，小子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're safe now. I got you here. You're safe. Let go, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.98,1:02:59.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,告诉我哪儿疼，告诉我哪儿疼     告诉我…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Tell me where it hurts. Tell me where it hurts. Tell me where...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.98,1:03:01.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你当时看见没有？     - 没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Did you see this? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.55,1:03:02.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,告诉我哪儿疼\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Tell me where it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.72,1:03:05.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,你哪里受伤了？你哪里受伤了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where does it hurt you? Where does it hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.39,1:03:09.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我听不见自己的声音     - 撞到脑袋了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I can't hear my voice. - Were you hit in the head?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.76,1:03:14.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,是不是撞到脑袋了？告诉我！     如果是，就告诉我！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Were you hit in the head? Tell me! You have to tell me if you were!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.40,1:03:16.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,我听不见自己的声音\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I can't hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.41,1:03:28.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,我得去指挥把火扑灭，在这里等我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have to go and deal with this now. You wait here for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.25,1:03:32.08,zimu,,0,0,0,,明白没？你在这儿等我     我就回来，我马上回来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You understand? You wait here for me. I'll be back. I'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.18,1:03:33.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你等着     - 你别走！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Wait here. - Don't leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.48,1:03:37.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会照顾你的，呆着别动，我来搞定\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going to take care of you. Wait. Stay here, son. I'm going to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.02,1:03:38.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 请你别走！     - 你会没事的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Don't leave! - You're going to be fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.02,1:03:40.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,在这儿等我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Wait for me here!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.12,1:03:43.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 把他按住，按住他     - 不要走！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hold him down. Hold him down. - Don't leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.36,1:03:47.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,得把绳缆割断，丹尼尔！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Got to break the cables, Daniel!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.13,1:03:50.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,给我一把锤子！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get me a hammer!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.31,1:03:58.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,给我一把锤子！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get me a hammer!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.71,1:04:02.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.74,1:04:29.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,后退！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.71,1:05:08.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 迈克尔     - 先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Michael! - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.11,1:05:10.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,带上戴夫，再叫两个人，去拿水管\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Take Dave and two of the fellas, pick up some hoses...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.65,1:05:14.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,比利，快去保护顶棚     温度太高就不好办了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Billy, protect the roof. Don't wait before it gets too hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.97,1:05:39.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,干嘛那样愁眉不展？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What are you looking so miserable about?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.74,1:05:42.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们脚下是油的海洋！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}There's a whole ocean of oil under our feet!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.71,1:05:45.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,它们只属于我，没有第二个主人！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No one can get at it except for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.10,1:06:33.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,H.W.还好么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}H.W. okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.70,1:06:36.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No, he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.54,1:06:40.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 他在哪儿？     - 在食堂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Where is he? - Mess room.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.07,1:08:23.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,别哼哼了，够了，H.W. ，别哼哼了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's enough now. That's enough, H.W. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.38,1:08:29.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,听见我说话么？能听见么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you hear me? Can you hear me in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.19,1:08:36.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.23,1:08:52.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 抓住他的脚     - 抓住脚了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Grab his legs. - I have his legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.10,1:08:54.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 不，不     - 别这样，小伙子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- No. Nope. - No, lad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.68,1:09:01.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,把那个给我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.58,1:09:06.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,稳住，就这样\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Steady. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.75,1:09:09.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 放松点孩子，放松     - 一会儿就好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Easy, boy. Easy. - Soon be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.25,1:09:13.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,好，就这样，现在换另一边     把他翻过来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yeah, and that's good. Now the other side. Turn him over.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.96,1:09:17.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,马上就好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Almost done.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.47,1:09:22.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.80,1:09:26.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,过来，结束了，都结束了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Come here. It's over. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.90,1:11:35.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们在旧金山认识什么人么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Who do we know in San Francisco
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.10,1:11:39.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,…或者洛杉矶，有谁可以帮忙的？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}or Los Angeles, who could work with...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.41,1:11:46.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们可以找个人，来当H.W.的老师\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You know, we could... Someone, a teacher for H.W.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.48,1:11:52.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,你来处理此事如何？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How could you figure out that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.68,1:11:57.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,打电话给…该死，那人叫什么来着？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, call... God damn it, what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.82,1:12:00.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,旧金山的鲍勃·布罗迪？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Bob Brody in San Francisco?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.29,1:12:04.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,打电话给鲍勃·布罗迪     让他找个老师过来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Call Bob Brody and get someone down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.97,1:12:12.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,我马上去办\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll do it right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.53,1:13:22.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候能拿到钱，丹尼尔？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}When do we get our money, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.84,1:13:32.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,你不是天命神医么？     你不是圣灵附体么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Aren't you a healer? And a vessel for the Holy Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.51,1:13:35.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么时候来把我儿子的耳朵治好？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}When are you coming over and make my son hear again?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.65,1:13:36.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,会不会啊你？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.88,1:13:38.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果让我为油井祈福     这种事根本不会发生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lf you had let me bless the well, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.98,1:13:41.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 丹尼尔…     - 你不该说这种话\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Daniel. - You shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.15,1:13:47.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,你还欠第三启示教会五千美金…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You owe the Church of the Third Revelation $5,000
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.40,1:13:47.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们当初约定好的！ 你还欠第三启示教会五千美金…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}as part of the arrangement that we made!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.45,1:13:50.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们当初约定好的！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.05,1:14:04.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,小矮人，想得美，门都没有！     让你尝尝泥浆浴的味道吧…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Don't even try it, you little runt! You splash around in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.72,1:14:13.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,这样才对，这样好多了…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's it, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.70,1:14:28.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会把你就地活埋，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going to bury you underground, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.41,1:14:35.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,把你活埋了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going to bury you underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.58,1:15:09.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,你太蠢了，埃布尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You are a stupid man, Abel.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.18,1:15:15.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,是你把生人请了进来     让他在我们头上撒野\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You've let someone come in here and walk all over us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.99,1:15:22.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,是你让他进来，让他在此胡作非为\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You let him in and do his work here,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.56,1:15:26.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,你太蠢了，破坏了原先美好的一切\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and you are a stupid man for what we could have had.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.70,1:15:30.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,是上帝让我这么做的，伊莱     我已经尽力了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I followed His word, Eli. I tried.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.74,1:15:33.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,你一直干坐着，根本没出力\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You didn't do anything but sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.84,1:15:37.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,你不仅懒惰，而且愚蠢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're lazy, and you're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.01,1:15:45.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,你想用愚蠢来换取上帝的救赎？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you think God is going to save you for being stupid?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.82,1:15:50.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,主不会救赎愚蠢的灵魂，埃布尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He doesn't save stupid people, Abel.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.76,1:15:58.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,就你做的这点破事，真想把你捏死     大蠢蛋！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I will tear you apart for what you've done, you stupid man!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.33,1:16:00.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,他怎么来的？你知不知道？     我知道！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How did he come here? Do you really know? I know!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.73,1:16:03.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 儿子，你别…不要…     - 不许吵！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Son, don't do this, please! - Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.50,1:16:08.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,闭上你的嘴，埃布尔！     是你那个蠢儿子干的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Shut your mouth, Abel! lt was your stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.67,1:16:12.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,是保罗让那家伙过来的，我知道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lt was Paul who told him to come here. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.71,1:16:14.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,他跟那家伙说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He went to him and he said,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.55,1:16:19.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,“我那愚蠢软弱的爸爸会让出土地的…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}"My stupid, weak father will give away his lots.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.39,1:16:22.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,快去搞定他吧”…     你果然就被人家轻松搞定了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}"Go and take him." And you let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.39,1:16:30.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,真是老鼠的儿子会打洞啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}A stupid father to a stupid son.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.17,1:16:37.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,出来吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.53,1:17:10.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,有什么事么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.74,1:17:13.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.37,1:17:17.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你是哪位？     - 我叫亨利\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Who's that? - My name is Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.08,1:17:19.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.65,1:17:22.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,我叫亨利\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.58,1:17:25.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,能为您做什么嘛？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.49,1:17:32.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是亨利·普莱维，来自丰迪拉克郡     (位于美国威斯康辛州)\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm Henry Plainview. I'm from Fond du Lac.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.83,1:17:38.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是你的兄弟，我们同父异母\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm your brother, from another mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.93,1:17:42.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,我父亲是欧内斯特\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ernest is my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.14,1:17:48.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.04,1:17:51.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,亨利\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.34,1:18:22.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 玛丽·布兰兹是你的母亲？     - 是的，先生，正是\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Mary Branch? Is that your mother? - Yes, sir, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.04,1:18:30.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,从报上听说了你的油井，还有你的成就\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I read about your gusher in the paper, about your success.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.35,1:18:33.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,听说我发家了，你就来找我了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You heard about my strike? You just show up?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.42,1:18:36.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们的父亲过世了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Our father's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.82,1:18:41.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,我听说欧内斯特死了，就想来找你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Ernest died, I heard. I wanted to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.16,1:18:42.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么时候死的？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}When?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.90,1:18:46.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,三个月前，安娜贝尔寄给我一封信\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Three months ago. I got a letter from Annabelle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.50,1:18:49.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的姐姐安娜贝尔？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My sister, Annabelle?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.37,1:18:55.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 她现在在哪儿？     - 还在老家，丰迪拉克郡\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Where is she? - Still at home. Fond du Lac.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.78,1:19:00.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,你大老远从威斯康辛过来     就为了告诉我这个？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You came all the way from Wisconsin to tell me this?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.38,1:19:03.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,我从新墨西哥州过来的     我在那儿待了一段时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm coming from New Mexico. I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.62,1:19:06.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,就为了过来找你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I came to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.62,1:19:09.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,你知道有我这个兄弟么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Did you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.80,1:19:19.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,你有证件么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you have identification?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.67,1:19:22.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,那封信你带了没？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you have this letter?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.92,1:19:47.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你从哪儿来？     - 新墨西哥州\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Where are you coming from? - From New Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.09,1:19:50.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,我知道，在哪个城市呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, I know, but from where?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.70,1:19:53.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,在银城，我在那儿待了两年\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, I know, but from where?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.01,1:19:54.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,Silver City. I've been there for two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.80,1:19:59.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,多年来我一直想成立自己的钻探队\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I was trying drilling of my own for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.74,1:20:06.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 在德克萨斯和路易斯安那租地探油     - 找到油了么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Getting leases in Texas. Louisiana. - Anything that produced?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.25,1:20:09.24,zimu,,0,0,0,,没有，比起你的成功，我毫无所获\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No. Not like your success, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.75,1:20:18.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 结婚了么？     - 没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Are you married? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.69,1:20:22.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,我曾坐过大牢，那日子真难熬\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I spent time in jail. I had a stretch of very bad time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.36,1:20:26.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,身无分文，在路易斯安那被人抓了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I had nothing. I was picked up in Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.07,1:20:31.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,身上拴着铁链，做了半年修路苦力\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I worked on a chain gang for six months building roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.24,1:20:35.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,真是不堪回首啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That was a very hard time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.18,1:20:40.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,你结婚了没有？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Are you married?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.25,1:20:44.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,你为了什么坐牢的？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What were you in jail for?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.78,1:20:49.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,说真的，虽然我也干过不少坏事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Believe it or not, for all the terrible things I've gotten myself into,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.42,1:20:52.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,但那次被抓的时候     我什么坏事也没干\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}when they picked me up, I hadn't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.06,1:20:56.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我也是罪有应得……\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But I've done my share of things
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.16,1:21:01.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,具体的罪恶么，恕我不能明述了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}that shouldn't be talked about.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.06,1:21:27.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,喝了它…喝了它！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Drink it. Drink it!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.70,1:22:11.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.67,1:22:43.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.77,1:22:50.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,你想要什么，亨利？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What do you want, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.98,1:22:54.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么也不要\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.52,1:23:01.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果不吝，我愿意为你打工\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If you can spare something, I can work for you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.82,1:23:06.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,不久后我可能还得继续漂泊     最后回老家丰迪拉克\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I know I'll keep moving, before long, to get back to Fond du Lac.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.16,1:23:09.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你有积蓄么？     - 有一点\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Do you have any money? - Some.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.60,1:23:12.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 但不多     - 跟我说实话\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Not much. - Just answer me directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.86,1:23:16.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,你刚才还说“什么也不要”     然后又说想留下干活\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You say "nothing," then you say you'd like to stay and work.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.57,1:23:21.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果你只说想留下干活     我听了会更舒服\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And it's better, I'd just like to hear you say you'd like to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.64,1:23:24.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想留下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.88,1:23:35.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,我干活很卖力的     我在钻油平台上干过，也修过铁路\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm a good worker. I worked cable tool rigs, built railroads.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.66,1:23:39.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,不需要你多加关照的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I won't need any favors.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.70,1:23:45.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.69,1:24:13.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,我妈妈知道这事么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   What did my mother know?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.46,1:24:18.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.70,1:24:23.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,也许她知道，但故意回避此事     装作不知，是否如此我不清楚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I don't know if she knew and looked the other way, if she never knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.97,1:24:27.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,你为何离开家？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.67,1:24:32.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,我只知道你和父亲不合\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I know you didn't get on with our father.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.85,1:24:41.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,我曾为地质勘探队工作过     并随他们一起去了堪萨斯…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I worked for Geological Survey and went to Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.02,1:24:47.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,我没法留在家里，觉得没法呆\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I couldn't stay there. I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.79,1:24:51.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢给自己找理由\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't like to explain myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.37,1:25:01.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 亨利，你容易动怒吗？     - 为了什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Are you an angry man, Henry? - About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.44,1:25:06.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,那你会嫉妒嘛？容易心生嫉妒嘛？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Are you envious? Do you get envious?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.51,1:25:09.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想没有…没有吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't think so, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.92,1:25:16.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的内心总在斗争\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have a competition in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.49,1:25:19.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不愿意见到其他人成功\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I want no one else to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.93,1:25:29.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 对大部分人，我都怀有恨意     - 我心中已经没有那些东西了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I hate most people. - That part of me is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.67,1:25:33.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,投入工作的热情，遭受挫折的懊恼\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Working and not succeeding,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.64,1:25:37.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,那些失败的往昔都已离我远去…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}all my failures have left me...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.68,1:25:42.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,我已经不在乎了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I just don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.25,1:25:46.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,在我心里的东西，在你心里也应该有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, if it's in me, it's in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.39,1:25:53.79,zimu,,0,0,0,,有很多次，我看着别人     找不到半点中意的地方\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}There are times when I look at people and I see nothing worth liking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.80,1:26:03.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想挣足够多的钞票，多到足以     远离俗世的烦扰，一个人自己过\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I want to earn enough money I can get away from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.87,1:26:11.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,你儿子怎么办？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What will you do about your boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.08,1:26:20.71,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.25,1:26:24.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,事情会发生变化也说不定\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Maybe it'll change.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.86,1:26:29.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,昨日是否会重回你身边？我不知道     也许没有人知道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Does your sound come back to you? I don't know. Maybe no one knows that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.39,1:26:33.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 连医生也不知道     - 孩子他妈呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Doctor might not know that. - Where's his mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.54,1:26:42.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不想谈论这事…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't want to talk about those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.91,1:26:48.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,我能看到人性最丑陋的那一面\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I see the worst in people, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.18,1:26:54.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,负面印象太多，甚至无需刻意回想\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't need to look past seeing them to get all I need.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.19,1:27:00.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,经过长年日积月累     我的恨意越蓄越深\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've built up my hatreds over the years, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.86,1:27:07.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,你来之后，在我的生活中     又打开了一扇崭新的窗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Having you here gives me a second breath of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.43,1:27:11.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不能再独自一个人战斗了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I can't keep doing this on my own
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.34,1:27:19.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,和这些人…抗争\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}with these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.25,1:28:01.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，丹尼尔，快醒醒！ 丹尼尔！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel! Daniel, wake up! Daniel!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.12,1:29:47.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,我得去和列车长说几句话\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just have to go and have a word with the conductor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.36,1:29:50.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,很快就回来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.60,1:29:55.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,你呆着…懂了么？待在这儿别动\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You stay here. You understand? You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.37,1:29:58.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.92,1:30:52.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,不！不~！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.46,1:30:55.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,不！！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.54,1:31:07.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 特尔福德！     - 普莱维\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Tilford! - Plainview.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.21,1:31:09.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,我兄弟亨利·普莱维，来自丰迪拉克\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is my brother, Henry Plainview from Fond du Lac.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.61,1:31:11.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,H.M. 特尔福德，很高兴认识你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}H.M. Tilford. Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.38,1:31:13.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 亨利·普莱维     - J.J.卡特\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Henry Plainview. J.J. Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.88,1:31:17.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.38,1:31:19.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我们开始？     - 好吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Shall we? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.19,1:31:29.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,你儿子情况如何？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How's your boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.53,1:31:32.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢关心     - 有什么要我们帮忙么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Thank you for asking. - Is there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.03,1:31:35.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,有你的关心就足够了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thanks for asking is enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.10,1:31:39.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,那么，你打算怎么办？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So what are your plans?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.87,1:31:44.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是在问我这里的地怎么卖？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is this about buying up my tracts here?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.24,1:31:45.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.41,1:31:48.24,zimu,,0,0,0,,电报里提的是我在野狼山的租约\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The cable was about my Coyote Hills lease.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.38,1:31:52.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 那份租约我们也想买     - 野狼山那份，你们开价多少？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We'd like that, too. - What's your offer on Coyote Hills?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.68,1:31:57.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 十五万美金，转让所有权利     - 没问题…接下来呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We'll offer 150,000 for full title. - That's a deal. What's next?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.09,1:32:02.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,你在小波士顿有11000英亩地     有一口出油井…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You have 11,000 acres in Little Boston. You have one proven well
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.76,1:32:04.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 但已受损…     - 有三口出油井\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- that was damaged... - I have three wells proven.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.40,1:32:08.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,看来你们调查不够，出油井一共三口\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You haven't been paying attention. That's three proven wells.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.74,1:32:14.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,你现在只需坐等收钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We'll make you a millionaire while you're sitting here
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.74,1:32:17.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们可以让你马上变成百万富翁\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}from one minute to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.91,1:32:21.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,卖了地之后我还能干嘛？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And what else would I do with myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.41,1:32:27.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你在问我？     - 我以后还能干嘛？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Are you asking me? - What else would I do with myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.42,1:32:30.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,照顾你儿子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Take care of your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.19,1:32:34.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,我又不了解你想干嘛\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't know what you would do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.26,1:32:39.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果此刻你是我     标准石油的人想来买你的地…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If you were me and Standard offered to buy what you had
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.86,1:32:42.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,还出价一百万美金，就会想问原因     为什么你们要这么做？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}for a million dollars, why? So, why?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.77,1:32:44.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,你知道原因\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.00,1:32:46.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,我建议你们学学其他人     凭自己的力量去挖去找\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yeah, you fellas should just scratch around in the dirt
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.94,1:32:50.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,而不是直接用钱去换别人辛勤的果实\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and find it like the rest of us, instead of buying up someone else's hard work.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.51,1:32:52.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,年轻人，我自己也挖过找过\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've scratched around the dirt, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.54,1:32:54.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们是不是准备上调运价啊？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You going to change your shipping costs?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.68,1:32:57.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们才不会操纵运价呢     这都是铁路公司的决定…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We don't dictate shipping costs. That's railroad business.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.68,1:33:01.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,铁路公司不是你们的产业？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You don't own the railroads?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.32,1:33:07.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,你们当然会啦，这点毫无疑问\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}'Course you do. Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.59,1:33:12.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,你准备把这些油送到哪儿去？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where you going to put it all?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.06,1:33:14.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,到哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.33,1:33:20.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果想造一条管线，然后和     联合石油做买卖，那就请便…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Build a pipeline? Make a deal with Union Oil? Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.47,1:33:22.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,但如果你的计划没能实现…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But if you can't pull it off,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.24,1:33:26.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,到时候守着偌大一片油田     却无处可去，岂不是很惨\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}you've got an ocean of oil under your feet with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.35,1:33:31.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,为什么不交给我们？     我们会让你发大财\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Why not turn it over to us? We'll make you rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.12,1:33:34.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,你可以腾出时间来照顾孩子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You spend time with your boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.49,1:33:37.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿的油田是一个惊人的发现\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's a great discovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.56,1:33:40.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在让我们来协助你吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.87,1:33:52.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,你竟然教训我该怎么带孩子…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Did you just tell me how to run my family?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.10,1:33:55.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的地现在能卖个好价钱     这一点也许更为重要\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lt might be more important now that you've proven the field
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.44,1:33:57.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们也愿出大钱买下你的地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and we're offering to buy you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.44,1:33:59.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,总有一天，我会进你的屋子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}One night I'm going to come to you, inside of your house,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.78,1:34:02.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,或是趁你熟睡的时候     用刀把你的喉咙割断\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}or wherever you're sleeping, and I'm going to cut your throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.85,1:34:04.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.78,1:34:06.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么啊？你是不是疯了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What are you talking about? Have you gone crazy?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.15,1:34:07.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你没听明白我说的？     - 我全听见了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Did you hear what I said? - I heard what you said,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.59,1:34:10.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你要干嘛？     - 不许教训我该怎样抚养儿子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- why did you say it? - You don't tell me about my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.15,1:34:12.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,你发什么疯，竟然威胁要割我喉咙？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Why are you acting insane and threatening to cut my throat?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.46,1:34:15.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 不许教训我该怎样抚养儿子     - 我根本没教训你！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- You don't tell me about my son. - I'm not telling you anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.63,1:34:19.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,请你理智一点     如果刚才我有所冒犯，我道歉\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm asking you to be reasonable. If I've offended you, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.56,1:34:21.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,那你就等着瞧好吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.51,1:34:33.71,zimu,,0,0,0,,这三千英亩是B.L. 哈珀的农场\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This parcel here is the 3,000-acre ranch owned by B.L. Harper.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.85,1:34:36.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是圣路易欧比斯珀郡的郡属土地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is San Luis Obispo County land.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.48,1:34:38.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,还有从这儿直到海岸     都被联合石油收购了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And from here to the coast, it's all Union Oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.42,1:34:41.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿呢？为什么我没买下这里？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What's this? Why don't I own this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.52,1:34:49.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 为什么我没买？     - 这是班迪的地产\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Why don't I own this? - That's the Bandy tract.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.86,1:34:53.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,就是那个在我们收购土地的时候     拒不合作的老头\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He was the holdout, when we were doing the buying.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.13,1:34:55.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,他想先和你谈谈\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He had hoped to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.77,1:35:03.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的管线不能绕过他的地盘么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can't you just build the pipeline around this tract?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.24,1:35:10.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要有这个能耐，就能把蒂哈查皮山     (加州南部横向山脉)再加长50英里了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can I build around 50 miles of Tehachapi mountains?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.45,1:35:12.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,别在我面前说蠢话，阿尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Don't be thick in front of me, Al.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.62,1:35:17.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我可以再去问他     - 不用，我亲自去和他说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I can go to him again. - No, I'll go and talk to the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.46,1:35:20.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,我去说，你们学着点\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll talk to him. Show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.20,1:35:26.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,就到这儿，亨利，你收拾一下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}All right. Pack it up, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.97,1:35:40.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我儿子的房间多大？     - 他和另一个孩子合住\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- How big is his room? - He's sharing with another boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.01,1:35:43.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 和谁？     - 一个比他大的孩子，12岁左右\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Who? - An older boy. About 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.95,1:35:46.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,名叫巴拉德，在那儿已经住了一年\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's been there for a year. Named Ballard.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.19,1:35:56.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 他的房间有多大？     - 不大不小，够两个人住的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- How big is the room? - It's a fair size. Got enough space.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.90,1:36:02.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,你要带亨利去见联合石油的人？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Are you taking Henry with you to meet Union Oil?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.41,1:36:18.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你是威廉·班迪的儿子？     - 他的孙子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Are you the son of William Bandy? - Grandson.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.08,1:36:20.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 他在么？     - 不，他出去了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Is he here? - No, he's out.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.99,1:36:22.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,他去哪儿了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.19,1:36:25.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,都说了他出去了，你有什么事？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Told you, he's out. Now, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.56,1:36:32.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是丹尼尔·普莱维     想和你爷爷谈谈他地产的事情\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm Daniel Plainview. I want to talk with him about his property.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.60,1:36:37.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 要谈些什么？     - 我还是和他亲自谈比较好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- About what? - I believe I'll talk with him about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.94,1:36:40.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你是个油矿主，对不对？     - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- You're that oilman, aren't you? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.51,1:36:42.47,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们不要你来挖油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We don't want you drilling out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.57,1:36:45.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,我也不想来啊…他什么时候回来？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't want it either. Now, when will he be back?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.08,1:36:47.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,几天以后吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Few days.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.25,1:36:49.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,跟他说，我想找他谈谈     不是挖油的事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Tell him I'd like to speak with him. Not about drilling.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.95,1:36:52.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,我一周后再来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And I'll be back in a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.29,1:39:13.42,zimu,,0,0,0,,把这根留在玻璃陈列柜里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Put that in a glass case.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.33,1:39:16.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,这杯酒敬给联合石油…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Here's to Union Oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.89,1:39:17.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,还有数百英里的输油管线…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Hundred miles of pipeline,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.10,1:39:20.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,以及本州所有的独立油矿主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and all the independent producers of this great state.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.63,1:39:21.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.76,1:39:49.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,在丰迪拉克老家有幢房子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   There's that house in Fond du Lac
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.36,1:39:54.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,是约翰·霍利斯特造的     你记得那房子么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   that John Hollister built. Do you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.50,1:40:00.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,小时候我觉得     那是我所见过的最漂亮的房子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I thought as a boy that was the most beautiful house I'd ever seen,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.04,1:40:02.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,梦想能拥有她\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.41,1:40:05.88,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想住在那房子里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I wanted to live in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.01,1:40:07.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,在里面吃饭…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And eat in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.41,1:40:10.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,在里面打扫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And clean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.02,1:40:17.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,打小我就想生很多孩子     让他们在房外奔跑戏耍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And even as a boy, I wanted to have children to run around in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.38,1:40:22.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在的你能把任何梦想变成现实\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You can have anything you'd like now, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.82,1:40:24.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,你应该去实现自己的梦想\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And you should.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.22,1:40:29.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你准备在哪儿建房子？   - 也许就建在这儿，在海边\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Where are you going to build it? - Here, maybe. Near the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.80,1:40:35.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,按照那幢房子的样式建？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Would you make it look like that house?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.30,1:40:43.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在如果再见到那幢房子   我也许会嗤之以鼻的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I think if I saw that house now, it'd make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.21,1:40:52.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们去大吃一顿吧，再找些女人乐乐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We can eat and get some women.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.65,1:40:57.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,就带她们去桃树舞厅…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Take them to the Peachtree dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.53,1:41:05.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,我说，先把自己灌个半醉   再带女人去桃树舞厅如何\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I say get liquored up and take them to the Peachtree dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.37,1:41:09.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.55,1:42:30.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,拜托，给我点钱吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can I have some money, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.36,1:42:40.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,给我点钱好吗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can I have some money, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.84,1:43:32.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想问你几件事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I want you to tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.01,1:43:37.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,问什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.22,1:43:41.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,希尔家旁边的农场叫什么名字？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What's the name of the farm next to the Hill House?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.73,1:43:57.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,希尔家旁边的农场叫什么名字？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What was the name of the farm next to the Hill House?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.94,1:44:03.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我记不起来了…   - 你是谁？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I can't remember... - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.88,1:44:08.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会走的，丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll leave, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.55,1:44:12.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,你到底是谁？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.45,1:44:16.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,我谁都不是\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm no one.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.06,1:44:20.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,让我起身吧，我马上消失\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just let me get up and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.83,1:44:24.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,我有兄弟么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do I have a brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.67,1:44:33.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,我在国王城遇见一个人   他说他是你的兄弟\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I met a man in King City who said he was your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.41,1:44:39.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们做了几个月的朋友\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We were friends for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.98,1:44:42.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,在国王城一起共事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Working in King City.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.15,1:44:48.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,他想来这儿找你，丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And he wanted to make his way to you, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.29,1:44:51.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,但当时我们没有钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We didn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.29,1:44:58.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,后来他得肺结核死了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He died of tuberculosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.00,1:45:01.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,不是死于暴力…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He wasn't harmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.87,1:45:05.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,也不是被杀的，就是正常的那种死亡\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Wasn't killed, nothing bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.94,1:45:09.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,但他跟我提起过你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But he told me about you,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.24,1:45:14.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,于是我借用了他的身份\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I just took his story,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.25,1:45:20.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,拿了他的日记\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}used his diary.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.69,1:45:24.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.29,1:45:29.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，我是你的朋友\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, I'm your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.83,1:45:34.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,我不想伤害你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm not trying to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.40,1:45:35.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,从来没想过…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.77,1:45:38.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,只想找口饭吃\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.84,1:45:40.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.69,1:48:51.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,哪位？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.46,1:48:53.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,我叫班迪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm Bandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.71,1:49:08.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,是你，你是…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.08,1:49:12.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,威廉·班迪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}William Bandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.02,1:49:18.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想租你的地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yeah, I'd like to lease your land.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.09,1:49:24.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,我曾邀请你去我那儿谈…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I had asked for you to come and talk to me before.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.76,1:49:27.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,可你在忙着租地，没来找我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}When you were leasing land.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.26,1:49:30.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,说的没错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.77,1:49:34.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,你知道，我儿子病得厉害，我抽不开身\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My boy's been very sick, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.44,1:49:37.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,那是在你儿子生病之前的事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This was before your boy got sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.08,1:49:45.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,我听说你想修一条管线\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, I know that you would like to build a pipeline
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.75,1:49:48.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,而且要经过我的土地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}through my property.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.52,1:49:52.65,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我听得没错吧？   - 完全正确\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Is that right, what I've heard? - It's absolutely right. And,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.36,1:49:54.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,那好…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}well...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.63,1:49:58.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,只是一根八英寸粗的管子，如果你点头   我们可以把它埋在地下……\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Eight inch pipe. It could be buried with your consent.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.00,1:50:01.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,我保证，绝不会给您带来任何影响\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I guarantee you absolutely no disruption...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.67,1:50:02.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,上帝…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}God.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.70,1:50:07.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,上帝把你要做的事告诉了我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}God has told me what you must do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.71,1:50:13.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要做的事？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And what is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.41,1:50:18.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,你得在耶稣基督的圣血中受洗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You should be washed in the blood of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.12,1:50:22.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我已经做了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.59,1:50:26.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,我已经受洗了，班迪先生   我早就受洗了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have been washed, Mr. Bandy. I have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.42,1:50:32.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是你唯一的救赎之道   是你得偿所愿的唯一方法\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's your only way to salvation. And your only way for what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.96,1:50:37.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,来第三启示教堂吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You can take it at the Church of the Third Revelation.
