Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.57,1:50:47.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,我希望你加入我们的教会\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like you to be part of our church.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.25,1:50:51.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,我付你五千美元\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll pay you $5,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.25,1:50:53.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,快来受洗吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Be baptized.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.09,1:50:58.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,请求主宽恕你的罪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Be forgiven for the sin that you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.19,1:51:08.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,你说的罪恶…是指什么，班迪先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What sin are you referring to, Mr. Bandy?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.23,1:51:11.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,因为我在这里钻井？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My sin of drilling?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.82,1:52:05.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,我真心希望每个人都能得到救赎   大家说是不是？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I truly wish everyone could be saved, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.96,1:52:07.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.99,1:52:10.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,只可惜事实并非如我们所愿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   I am afraid that's just not the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.56,1:52:16.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,号称所有人都能得救，那是谎言   大家说是不是？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The doctrine of universal salvation is a lie, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.20,1:52:18.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是骗人的   - 是骗人的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- It's a lie. - It's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.94,1:52:23.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,我希望每个人都能得救，但这不可能！   不可能人人都得救！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I wish everyone could be saved, but they won't. No, they won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.84,1:52:27.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,要想得救，你只有…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You will never be saved if you...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.41,1:52:29.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,接受圣血的洗礼！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Reject the blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.21,1:52:31.37,zimu,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.45,1:52:36.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿有寻求救赎的罪人么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now, is there a sinner here looking for salvation?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.59,1:52:41.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,我指新来的人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}A new member?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.66,1:52:47.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,我再问一遍：\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll ask it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.43,1:52:52.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,这儿有寻求主赦的罪人么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Is there a sinner here looking for God?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.27,1:52:53.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.54,1:52:58.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,让我来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.21,1:53:03.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的光临，丹尼尔兄弟\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you for coming, brother Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.08,1:53:07.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Thank you, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.89,1:53:13.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们这儿有位希望得到救赎的罪人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have a sinner with us here who wishes for salvation!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.09,1:53:17.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 丹尼尔，你是罪人么   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Daniel, are you a sinner? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.79,1:53:20.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,主听不见你的话，丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Lord can't hear you, Daniel.
