Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.24,1:53:27.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 好的   - 跪对上帝\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes. - Down on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.64,1:53:29.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,向他祈祷\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Pray to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.61,1:53:34.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,抬头向上苍，说出你的罪过\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Look up to the sky and say it.
