Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.78,1:53:45.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，你为这里带来了利益和财富\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, you've come here and you've brought good and wealth,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.39,1:53:49.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,但也带来了恶习，你是个堕落者\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}but you have also brought your bad habits as a backslider.
