Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.07,1:54:03.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我是一个罪人   - 大声说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I am a sinner. - Say it louder.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.07,1:54:06.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我是一个罪人   - 我是一个罪人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I am a sinner. - I am a sinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.94,1:54:08.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,再大声点，丹尼尔！我是一个罪人！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Louder, Daniel! I am a sinner!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.98,1:54:11.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我是一个罪人！   - 主啊，我错了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I am a sinner. - I am sorry, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.02,1:54:14.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 主啊，我错了！   - 请赐我圣血吧！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I am sorry, Lord. - I want the blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.32,1:54:17.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 请赐我圣血吧！   - 你舍弃了自己的孩子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I want the blood. - You have abandoned your child.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.45,1:54:19.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,我舍弃了自己的孩子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I have abandoned my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.86,1:54:22.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我绝不再甘堕落   - 我绝不再甘堕落\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I will never backslide. - I will never backslide.
