Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.46,1:54:29.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我曾迷失，现又重归本我   - 我舍弃了自己的孩子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I was lost, but now I'm found. - I have abandoned my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.13,1:54:34.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,跟我说，快说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Say it. Say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.40,1:54:37.43,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我舍弃了自己的孩子   - 大声点，说大声点！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I abandoned my child. - Say it louder. Say it louder!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.54,1:54:39.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,我舍弃了自己的孩子！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've abandoned my child!
