Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.15,1:55:23.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,你愿接受耶稣基督为救世主么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you accept Jesus Christ as your Savior?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.85,1:55:25.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, I do.
