Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.91,1:56:26.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家，兄弟\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Welcome home, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.48,1:56:30.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,好了……到此为止吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's enough. That's enough, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.19,1:56:37.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,他得自己将圣灵引入体内\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He must take the spirit in on his own.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.13,1:56:41.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们又多了一位新的兄弟\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We have a new member.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.13,1:56:44.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是的，兄弟   - 哈利路亚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes, brother. - Hallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.37,1:56:46.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 哈利路亚   - 阿门\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hallelujah. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.50,1:56:50.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 普莱维先生非常慷慨   - 亲爱的玛丽…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- My sweet Mary. - Mr. Plainview has been generous
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.71,1:56:53.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,他愿捐出五千美金\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}enough to make a $5,000 donation
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.58,1:56:56.60,zimu,,0,0,0,,捐给教会，虽然这笔钱还没到帐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}to the church which we are still waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.75,1:58:12.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,这感觉真好，这感觉真好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That does me good. That does me good.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.16,1:58:15.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家，儿子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Welcome home, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.59,1:58:20.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家，儿子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Welcome home, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.50,1:58:26.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,这位是乔治·雷诺兹，聋校的老师\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This here's George Reynolds. Teacher from the deaf school.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.67,1:58:29.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 普莱维先生   - 弗莱彻\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Mr. Plainview. - Fletcher.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.48,1:58:34.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,你都变得这么重了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're too heavy for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.65,1:58:40.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,想吃点东西么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you want to get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.55,1:58:45.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,看见没，那边就是输油管线   一直通到大海\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's the pipeline, see? All the way to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.98,1:59:08.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.42,1:59:17.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,我爱你，儿子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I love you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.09,1:59:21.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,让我好好看看你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let's take a look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.49,1:59:26.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,好了，够了，够了…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}All right. That's it, that's it. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.42,1:59:53.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,让我们弄点好吃的吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Let's get some decent food inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.82,1:59:57.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们到这儿来，就是来   吃一顿丰盛高档的大餐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's all we need here is a good, strong, expensive meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.26,1:59:59.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,你饿了么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.83,2:00:01.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 服务生？   - 您好，先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Waiter? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.06,2:00:05.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,两份牛排，一杯威士忌   给这位年轻人来一杯水\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Two steaks, a whiskey, and water for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.70,2:00:09.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 再来一杯羊奶   - 好的，先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- And goat's milk. - Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.05,2:00:18.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们请了位老师来帮你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We're going to have this teacher help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.55,2:00:24.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,他会照顾好我们大家的，听明白了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's going to help take care of all of this. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.15,2:00:26.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,我需要你，需要你的帮助\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}'Cause I need you. Need your help.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.99,2:00:30.95,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在我们的公司已一切就绪   过来…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Got everything we need now to build this company. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.77,2:00:40.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,下午好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.62,2:00:58.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你好么？   - 很高兴再次见到你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- How are you doing? - It's nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.79,2:01:01.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我们需要四个人的桌子   - 我马上派人安排\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- We need four. - I'll have them right up.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.76,2:01:07.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 下午好，丹尼尔   - 哦，特尔福德\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Good afternoon, Daniel. - Tilford.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.86,2:01:09.23,zimu,,0,0,0,,下午好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.80,2:01:16.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 你好，我是H.M.特尔福德！   - 用不着那么大声\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Hello! H.M. Tilford! - You don't have to shout.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.11,2:01:19.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你们\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.21,2:01:26.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,小波士顿这儿不错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's good to be in Little B.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.75,2:01:31.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 这里应该下点雨   - 是啊，没错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Could use some rain out here. - Yeah, we could.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.92,2:01:35.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我们的饮料来了   - R.J.，伦敦烤肉味道如何？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- There we go. - R.J., how's the London broil?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.16,2:01:37.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们比这些人先要的饮料\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Believe we ordered these drinks before those people.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.93,2:01:42.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,- R.J.，说说看，这儿的烤肉如何？   - 对不起，先生们，我很抱歉\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- R.J., tell us. How's the London broil? - Excuse me, gentlemen. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.27,2:01:48.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,先生，我很抱歉   你们的牛排马上就来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am sorry about that, sir. I'll have your steaks right out.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.05,2:02:00.61,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 听说海龟汤很不错   - 是么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- So that green turtle soup is fantastic. - Is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.75,2:02:02.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,非常美味\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lt's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.42,2:02:08.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,听上去合我胃口\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.52,2:02:14.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,标准石油愿出一百万美元   收购我在小波士顿的租地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So Standard offered us a million dollars for the Little Boston leases.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.36,2:02:17.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,我告诉特尔福德，让他一边去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I told H.M. Tilford where he could shove that.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.37,2:02:21.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,于是我找了联合石油做生意！   还修了一条管线！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And we made a deal with Union! On the pipeline!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.10,2:02:25.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,把脚下的这片油海慢慢运出去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And that whole ocean of oil underneath our fields.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.67,2:02:27.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 15万美金   - 好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...$150,000. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.44,2:02:29.74,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们需要钱开井\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We needed the money to drill.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.88,2:02:32.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 那人是谁？   - 我去和他说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Who is this guy? - I go out to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.21,2:02:34.98,zimu,,0,0,0,,他的地里有油，我们想买下所有权\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's getting oil on the property. We're trying to make a claim on it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.12,2:02:37.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后给他一百万报价\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Offered him a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.15,2:02:40.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 他却一口回绝   - 好了，我饿了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Turned us down flat. - Well, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.49,2:02:45.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,桔子馅饼，土豆泥，还有青豆…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Orange fritters, mashed potatoes, green peas.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.23,2:02:47.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 都是这种东西？   - 好罢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- All the way around? - All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.60,2:02:51.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,等一等\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.74,2:02:58.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,请你往那边看\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I want you to look over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.11,2:03:00.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 丹尼尔，我来介绍一下…   - 往那边看，看见没？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Daniel, let me introduce... - Look over there. You see?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.04,2:03:03.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,那是我儿子，你看见他了么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's my son. See him?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.25,2:03:05.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我看见了   - 你看见了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes. - Do you see?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.92,2:03:09.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,我看见他了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I see him.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.22,2:03:13.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,别教训我该怎么抚养后代\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You don't tell me how to raise my family.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.22,2:03:18.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,我警告你，别教训我该怎么抚养后代\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I told you not to tell me how to raise my family.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.23,2:03:22.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.93,2:03:24.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,你现在看见什么了？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So what do you see?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.77,2:03:29.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我很高兴你的生意能…   - 是的，我和联合石油的生意成了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'm very happy for you that the deal... - Yes, I made a deal with Union.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.04,2:03:32.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我的儿子也很快乐，很安全   - 恭喜你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- My son is happy. He's safe. - Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.51,2:03:35.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 现在由我照顾他，所以…   - 那样很好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'm taking care of him now, so... - Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.98,2:03:39.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,你看上去就像个傻瓜   是不是啊，特尔福德？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You look like a fool, don't you, Tilford?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.65,2:03:47.49,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是的   - 是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.33,2:03:50.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,说“是”就对了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.89,2:03:53.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,请见谅，先生们\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Excuse me, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.70,2:03:56.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,请原谅我，先生们   也请原谅他\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Excuse me, gentlemen. Excuse him, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.47,2:04:03.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,我早告诉你我会这么做了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I told you what I was going to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.42,2:04:14.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的儿子…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My son.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.70,2:04:36.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,桑迪先生，听说你要离开我们教区\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Sunday, I understand that you're leaving our fair community.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.14,2:04:39.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 是的，我打算出去传道   - 你要去哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes, I'm going on a mission. - Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.38,2:04:41.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,去石油谷和塔夫脱   然后到贝克斯菲尔德\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Oildale, Taft, and then on to Bakersfield.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.68,2:04:44.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,那么，我想说…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Well, I want you to know...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.15,2:04:46.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,三刻钟时间\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Three quarters of an hour.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.15,2:04:47.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,你为我们做了很多\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...you done a great job for us.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.82,2:04:50.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，我在祈祷时会祝福你的   - 非常感谢你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Thank you. You will be in my prayers. - I thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.79,2:04:54.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,联合石油公司，加州圣保拉市\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Union Oil Company, Santa Paula, California.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.05,2:07:05.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,“妇人说，先生，请把这水赐给我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}"The woman saith unto him, 'Sir, give me this water
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.09,2:07:06.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,1927年   “妇人说，先生，请把这水赐给我
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.85,2:07:07.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,1927年\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}"'and I shall thirst not, neither come hither to draw."'
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.89,2:07:12.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,叫我不渴，也不用来这么远打水”   1927年
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.09,2:07:12.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,叫我不渴，也不用来这么远打水”
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.36,2:08:56.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,进来，进来吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Come in, come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.79,2:09:25.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们能单独谈谈么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Can we be alone?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.13,2:09:28.82,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是我最亲密的伙伴，我对他没有秘密\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is my closest associate. He hears everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.90,2:09:40.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我还是想和你私下交谈   - 你又张不了嘴\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'd prefer to speak to you in private. - You can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.08,2:09:43.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,那就用你的手比划吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So why don't you flap your hands about
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.41,2:09:46.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,让那谁谁代你说   这些日子你都去哪儿了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and have what's-his-name tell me where you've been.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.96,2:09:57.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,你以为我不知道你小子去了哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Or do you think I don't know?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.17,2:10:14.40,zimu,,0,0,0,,关于此事我很难开口…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is hard for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.51,2:10:19.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,先要说的是，我非常非常爱你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll tell you first, I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.92,2:10:26.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,从你身上，我学会了热爱事业\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've learned to love what I do because of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.36,2:10:32.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,我准备离开这里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm leaving here.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.66,2:10:35.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要去墨西哥\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.13,2:10:39.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,我还会带上玛丽，去墨西哥\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm taking Mary, and I'm going to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.77,2:10:42.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,我很想念在外工作的生活\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I miss working outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.91,2:10:45.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,也很想念油田\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I miss the fields.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.74,2:10:50.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,可能过不多久\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It'll only be for a time,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.08,2:10:54.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,我会成立自己的钻探队\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}for me to do my own drilling
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.12,2:10:58.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后开创自己的公司\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and start my own company.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.26,2:11:05.72,zimu,,0,0,0,,是时候改变一下了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's time to make a change.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.77,2:11:21.27,zimu,,0,0,0,,这样一来，你我就变成对手了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This makes you my competitor.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.25,2:11:30.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 不不，我没有那个意思…   - 你就是这个意思，孩子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- No. No, it's not like that. - It is like that, boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.59,2:11:33.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,你自己的公司？不错嘛！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Your own company, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.99,2:11:35.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.83,2:11:39.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,在墨西哥？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}In Mexico?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.06,2:11:42.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.23,2:11:47.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,犯什么浑啊你！到底想干嘛？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You are making such a misstep. So, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.34,2:11:52.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,我知道我们有很多事意见不一致\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I know you and I have disagreed over many things.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.61,2:11:57.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,我宁愿当你是父亲，而不是合作伙伴\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd rather keep you as my father than my partner.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.05,2:11:59.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,那就说出来！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Then say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.65,2:12:01.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果你有话要说，我希望你自己开口…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If you've got something to say to me, then say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.45,2:12:05.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,我想听你说，不想你身后的那条狗叫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like to hear you speak instead of your little dog.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.24,2:12:25.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要和妻子一起去墨西哥\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going to Mexico with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.91,2:12:29.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要离开你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm going away from you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.08,2:12:37.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,看来这不难，是不是？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That wasn't so hard, was it?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.69,2:12:42.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,你所做的会毁了我们两个\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Killing us with what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.23,2:12:48.69,zimu,,0,0,0,,你正在扼杀我心目中的好儿子形象\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're killing my image of you as my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.83,2:12:52.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,你太固执了，听不进别人的建议\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You are stubborn. You won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.33,2:12:54.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,你不是我的儿子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're not my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:54.74,2:12:57.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,请别那样说，我知道你是随口说说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Please don't say that. I know you don't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.04,2:13:02.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是事实，你不是我的儿子   从来都不是\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's the truth. You're not my son. You never have been.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.38,2:13:05.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是一个孤儿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're an orphan!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.88,2:13:10.11,zimu,,0,0,0,,听说过这个词么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Did you ever hear that word?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.62,2:13:13.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,把我的话告诉他\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Tell him what I said.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:14.29,2:13:17.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,你今天所作的，和你的身份蛮配\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You operated here today like one.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.89,2:13:21.36,zimu,,0,0,0,,我早该想到有这一天\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I should have seen this coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.86,2:13:27.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,我早该知道，经过了这么多年…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I should have known that, under this all, these past years
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.84,2:13:31.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,你对我的怨气一点点积累   最后变成了新的仇恨\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}you've been building new hate for me, piece by piece.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.34,2:13:34.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,我甚至都不知道你是谁   你身上根本没我的影子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I don't even know who you are because you have none of me in you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.08,2:13:37.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是别人的孩子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're someone else's.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.38,2:13:42.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的愤怒，你的怨意\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This anger. Your maliciousness.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.95,2:13:46.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,还有你对我的消极态度…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Backwards dealings with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.52,2:13:52.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是装在篮子里的孤儿   是我从沙漠中捡来的…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're an orphan from a basket in the middle of the desert.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.30,2:14:00.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,收养你不为别的，只为买地时   身边有张俏脸蛋，诓人容易些\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And I took you for no other reason than I needed a sweet face to buy land.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:01.77,2:14:03.53,zimu,,0,0,0,,你听见没有？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.77,2:14:06.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在你总算知道真相了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So now you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.85,2:14:14.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,看着我！你比烂货更下贱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Look at me! You're lower than a bastard.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.11,2:14:43.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,在你体内根本没有我的血   你不过是篮子里装的小烂货\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You have none of me in you. You're just a bastard from a basket.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.26,2:14:57.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,感谢主，我体内没有你的血\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I thank God I have none of you in me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.43,2:15:06.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,你不是我儿子   只是个不起眼的对手\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Not my son. Just a little piece of competition.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.80,2:15:10.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,篮子里的烂货\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Bastard from a basket.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.31,2:15:15.50,zimu,,0,0,0,,篮子里的烂货！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Bastard from a basket!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.89,2:15:26.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,你是篮子里的烂货！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You're a bastard from a basket!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.95,2:16:30.75,zimu,,0,0,0,,起来，丹尼尔先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Get up, Mr. Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.12,2:16:36.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}   Mr. Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.66,2:16:41.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔先生，有人来拜访\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Daniel, you've got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.90,2:16:46.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,醒醒，丹尼尔先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Wake up, Mr. Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.47,2:16:51.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.59,2:17:06.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,你可以走了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You can leave us now.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.83,2:17:15.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.17,2:17:20.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:22.94,2:17:26.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔·普莱维，房子着火了！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel Plainview, the house is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.81,2:17:33.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔兄弟， 是我，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Brother Daniel, it's Eli.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.03,2:17:47.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,是你，是你啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, it is. Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:49.86,2:17:51.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,来杯酒吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'll make us a drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.37,2:18:01.54,zimu,,0,0,0,,你的家真是个奇迹\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Your home is a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:02.81,2:18:04.08,zimu,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.08,2:18:04.44,zimu,,0,0,0,,真是太漂亮了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.08,2:18:07.14,zimu,,0,0,0,,愿主保佑这里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}God bless it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:07.28,2:18:11.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,这些日子我一直在各地传道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've been spreading His word far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:12.55,2:18:14.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,广为传道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:16.16,2:18:18.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,为了主我四处奔波\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}So much travel for Him.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.63,2:18:26.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,我还曾通过无线电散播福音\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've been working in radio.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:28.74,2:18:32.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,发生了那么多事情…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, so much... So much has been happening.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:33.74,2:18:39.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,回来看到你一切都好，我很高兴\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}To be here and find you and see you well is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.35,2:18:41.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,正好有机会，我们叙叙旧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And we have a chance to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.06,2:18:57.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,不用了，谢谢你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:15.25,2:19:16.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的兄弟\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.19,2:19:21.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，我的兄弟，我们是姻亲啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, my brother by marriage.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.46,2:19:27.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,多少年的老朋友…都这么多年了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We're such old friends. So much time.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.07,2:19:37.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,经历了这么多起起落落…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Things go up, things go down,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:37.27,2:19:41.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,至少还有主总在我们身旁\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}but at least the Lord is always around.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:43.18,2:19:45.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,我们有过得意，也有过失意，不是么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}We've seen ups and downs, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:49.65,2:19:52.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,你现在失意么，伊莱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Are things down for you right now, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:53.99,2:19:55.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:57.83,2:20:00.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我的确带来了一个悲伤的消息\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But I do come with some sad news.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.20,2:20:04.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,还记得班迪先生么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Perhaps you remember Mr. Bandy?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:07.57,2:20:10.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,他老人家已升入天国了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Bandy has passed on to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:11.84,2:20:15.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,他活了99岁，愿神保佑\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He lived to be 99 years old, God bless him.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.71,2:20:19.58,zimu,,0,0,0,,班迪先生有个孙子   他叫威廉，你见过么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Bandy has a grandson. Have you met his grandson, William?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.58,2:20:25.18,zimu,,0,0,0,,威廉班迪是我们最好的兄弟之一…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}William Bandy is one of the finest members we have
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.29,2:20:27.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,为第三启示教会奉献了很多\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}at the Church of the Third Revelation.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:27.96,2:20:31.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,他很想去好莱坞拍电影\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's eager to come to Hollywood to be in movies.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.73,2:20:34.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,他长得不错\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He is very good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.10,2:20:42.09,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得他能红   - 那样很好嘛\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- And I do think he will have success. - That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.24,2:20:47.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,要不要我找他谈谈？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Would you like me to speak with him?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:54.42,2:20:59.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，我问你是否愿意…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, I'm asking if you'd like to have business
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.29,2:21:01.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,和第三启示教会做笔交易\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}with the Church of the Third Revelation
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.62,2:21:05.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,在小班迪的那一千英亩地上钻井采油\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}in developing this lease on young Bandy's 1,000-acre tract.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.33,2:21:09.92,zimu,,0,0,0,,小波士顿的这块地，我可以给你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm offering you to drill
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.06,2:21:13.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,面积非常大，还没人开发过！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}on one of the great undeveloped fields of Little Boston.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.64,2:21:17.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我很高兴和你合作   - 你愿意？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'd be happy to work with you. - You would?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.37,2:21:22.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,是是，当然，那样太好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, yes, of course. That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:22.34,2:21:25.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,但我有个条件\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But there is one condition for this work.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.41,2:21:26.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,好吧你说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:28.98,2:21:32.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,我希望你亲口跟我说   你是一个冒牌的先知\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like you to tell me that you are a false prophet.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:37.89,2:21:43.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,我希望你亲口跟我说   你是，而且从来都是个冒牌的先知\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'd like you to tell me that you are, and have been a false prophet.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.50,2:21:46.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,所谓的上帝也不过是迷信\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}And that God is a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:52.97,2:21:54.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是谎言\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:57.58,2:22:00.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,这是谎言，我不能说谎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's a lie. I cannot say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:14.40,2:22:16.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候开始钻井？   - 很快就能开始\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- When can we begin to drill? - Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.93,2:22:18.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,那多久之后能开始出油呢？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}How long will it take to bring in the well?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.67,2:22:20.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,不会很久的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}lt shouldn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:20.70,2:22:23.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,我要十万美金作为签字费…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I would like a $100,000 signing bonus,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.07,2:22:27.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,外加先前欠的五千元，还有利息\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}plus the five that is owed to me with interest.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.04,2:22:29.81,zimu,,0,0,0,,恩，这样才公平嘛\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's only fair.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:35.58,2:22:40.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知   上帝是迷信的产物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet, and God is a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:40.49,2:22:43.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果你这么认为，我就这么说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If that's what you believe, then I will say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.56,2:22:47.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 要用令人信服的语气说出来   - 丹尼尔…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Say it like you mean it. - Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:47.60,2:22:49.93,zimu,,0,0,0,,要用你布道的口气说\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Say it like it's your sermon.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.10,2:22:54.73,zimu,,0,0,0,,不要笑\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Don't smile.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.51,2:23:02.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.51,2:23:05.84,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 上帝是迷信的产物   - 何不站起来说？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- God is a superstition. - Why don't you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:08.92,2:23:10.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,把杯子放下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Put your glass down.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.10,2:23:26.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.80,2:23:29.86,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 上帝是迷信的产物   - 伊莱，停一下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- God is a superstition. - Eli, stop.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:29.97,2:23:35.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,把这里想作是你的教堂   面前还坐满了信徒…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Just imagine this is your church here and you have a full congregation, so...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:37.91,2:23:41.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知   上帝是迷信的产物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet. God is a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:41.78,2:23:43.38,zimu,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.45,2:23:48.32,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知   上帝是迷信的产物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet. God is a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.42,2:23:49.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,坐在后面的人听不清楚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}They can't hear you at the back.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.69,2:23:53.06,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知   上帝是迷信的产物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet. God is a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.19,2:23:54.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.36,2:23:58.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知！   上帝是迷信的产物！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet! God is a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.10,2:24:00.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:00.90,2:24:04.63,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是一个冒牌的先知！   上帝是迷信的产物！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am a false prophet! God is a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.84,2:24:08.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,那片地方的油已经采完了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Those areas have been drilled.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.28,2:24:12.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:12.81,2:24:15.41,zimu,,0,0,0,,那些地方的油已经采完了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Those areas, they've been drilled.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.02,2:24:20.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 不，没有   - 是采完了…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- No, they haven't. - Yes, it's...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:20.66,2:24:21.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的抽水效应，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It's called drainage, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.12,2:24:26.96,zimu,,0,0,0,,听着，那农场周围的地都是我的   所以我早把他地下的油给抽干了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}See, I own everything around it, so, of course, I get what's underneath it.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:28.43,2:24:31.59,zimu,,0,0,0,,那儿连个采油平台都没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}But there are no derricks there.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:31.73,2:24:34.10,zimu,,0,0,0,,是班迪的地…知道我说哪儿么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}This is the Bandy tract. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:34.24,2:24:36.20,zimu,,0,0,0,,还没明白过来，伊莱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Do you understand, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:36.94,2:24:40.17,zimu,,0,0,0,,似乎没搞清楚的是你   明白没有？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's more to the point. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.27,2:24:45.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,我喝光了你杯子里的水，我把它喝光了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I drink your water. I drink it up every day.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.68,2:24:50.91,zimu,,0,0,0,,我每天都在吸班迪地皮底下的圣血\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I drink the blood of Lamb from Bandy's tract.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.19,2:24:58.28,zimu,,0,0,0,,现在你可以坐下了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}You can sit down again.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:16.44,2:25:17.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,哦，丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.05,2:25:22.04,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.92,2:25:27.22,zimu,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:29.86,2:25:34.19,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我已经无路可走了   - 我知道\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I am in desperate times. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:34.30,2:25:37.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我需要一个朋友   - 是啊，你当然需要了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I need a friend. - Yes. Of course, you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:37.57,2:25:39.16,zimu,,0,0,0,,我犯了罪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've sinned.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:40.94,2:25:44.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,我需要帮助，我是罪人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I need help. I'm a sinner.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.17,2:25:48.77,zimu,,0,0,0,,我做梦也不曾想   竟让魔鬼夺了魂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I've let the devil grab hold of me in ways I never imagined.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:48.88,2:25:50.31,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是个不折不扣的罪人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm so full of sin.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:50.41,2:25:53.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,上帝有时候会考验我们，不是么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}The Lord sometimes challenges us, doesn't He, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.82,2:25:55.78,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 哦，丹尼尔，没错…   - 是啊，他会的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Yes, He does, Daniel. - Yes, He does.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:55.88,2:25:58.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,是的，他考验了我啊啊啊！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, He does!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:58.62,2:26:00.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,是啊他考验了你啊啊啊啊！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Yes, He does!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:01.82,2:26:07.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,最近的经济大危机   他连一声提醒都没给我…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's completely failed to alert me to the recent panic in our economy.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.50,2:26:09.66,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 还有这件事…   - 哦，小可怜\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- And this... - Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.80,2:26:16.46,zimu,,0,0,0,,我必须得弄到钱，丹尼尔   我必须、非得、一定要弄到钱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I must have this, Daniel. I must, I must, I must have this.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.60,2:26:18.87,zimu,,0,0,0,,我需要这笔钱填补投资黑洞\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}My investments have...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.97,2:26:24.00,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，我不想烦你，可要是能   抓到主的手乞求帮助，我早去了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, I won't bore you, but if I could grab the Lord's hand for help I would,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.11,2:26:27.01,zimu,,0,0,0,,但他总是不吭声…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}but He does these things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.11,2:26:31.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,故作神秘，让我们干等着…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}These mysteries that He presents, and while we wait...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.35,2:26:34.51,zimu,,0,0,0,,干等着他发话！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}While we wait for His word!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:34.66,2:26:37.62,zimu,,0,0,0,,因为上帝选中的兄弟不是你，伊莱\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Because you're not the chosen brother, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:37.34,2:26:37.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,Because you're not the chosen brother, Eli.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:40.03,2:26:43.83,zimu,,0,0,0,,他选中了你的双胞胎兄弟，保罗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}'Twas Paul who was chosen.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:44.73,2:26:47.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,是保罗找到我，告诉我到这儿来   你只是个傻子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He found me and told me about your land. You're just a fool.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:47.80,2:26:50.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 为什么要提起保罗？   - 你兄弟没做到的，我做到了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Why are you talking about Paul? - I did what your brother couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:50.74,2:26:53.26,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 别跟我说这些   - 我击溃了你，打垮了你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Don't say this to me. - I broke you and I beat you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.18,2:26:56.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,是保罗他告诉我有你这么个人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}It was Paul told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.11,2:27:01.57,zimu,,0,0,0,,他才是先知，他才是智者   他早知道地底下藏着宝藏\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He's the prophet. He's the smart one. He knew what was there
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.68,2:27:04.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,是他找到了我，让我去把宝藏挖出来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and he found me to take it out of the ground.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.15,2:27:07.25,zimu,,0,0,0,,你知道最有趣的是什么？   听着，听好了…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Know what the funny thing is? Listen, listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.12,2:27:12.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,我给了他一万美元，全是现金   事实就是这样\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I paid him $10,000 cash in hand. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.06,2:27:16.39,zimu,,0,0,0,,他现在自己开了家公司   小生意蒸蒸日上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}He has his own company now. Prosperous little business.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:16.50,2:27:20.02,zimu,,0,0,0,,旗下三口油井，周入五千美金\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Three wells producing, $5,000 a week.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.10,2:27:25.90,zimu,,0,0,0,,你个大哭包，别哭哭啼啼了   我不想再听你胡扯\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Stop crying, you sniveling ass. Stop your nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:27.11,2:27:29.94,zimu,,0,0,0,,伊莱，其实你只是你兄弟出生时   顺带落出的那个胎盘\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- You're just the afterbirth, Eli. - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.05,2:27:33.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 不   - 从你母亲产后的秽物中滑落出来\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That slithered out on your mother's filth.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.81,2:27:35.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.25,2:27:39.45,zimu,,0,0,0,,他们应该把你装在玻璃瓶里   搁置在壁炉架上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}They should've put you in a glass jar on the mantelpiece.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:41.16,2:27:44.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,保罗在妈妈身上吸奶的时候，你在哪儿？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where were you when Paul was suckling at his mother's teat?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.66,2:27:46.15,zimu,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿啊？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:46.29,2:27:50.99,zimu,,0,0,0,,谁把你养大的，可怜的伊莱？   班迪家的一头母猪么？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Who was nursing you, poor Eli? One of Bandy's sows?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:51.13,2:27:54.07,zimu,,0,0,0,,那块地我早就吃干净了   对此你一点办法也没有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That land has been had. Nothing you can do about it. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:54.17,2:27:56.33,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 请你买下这块地皮吧…   - 你输了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- lf you would just take this lease... - You lose.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:56.47,2:27:59.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,抽水效应！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Drainage!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:00.74,2:28:04.30,zimu,,0,0,0,,知道抽水效应么，伊莱！   你个小毛孩子…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Drainage, Eli, you boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:05.45,2:28:08.35,zimu,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，已经抽干了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Drained dry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:09.58,2:28:11.68,zimu,,0,0,0,,如果你有一杯奶昔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}If you have a milkshake
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.79,2:28:14.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,我也有一杯奶昔…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I have a milkshake,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.66,2:28:17.85,zimu,,0,0,0,,我还有一根吸管，就在那儿   那是一根吸管，看到没？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and I have a straw, there it is. That's the straw, you see?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.96,2:28:19.52,zimu,,0,0,0,,看好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Watch it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:20.96,2:28:27.89,zimu,,0,0,0,,我的吸管穿过房间…\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Now my straw reaches across the room
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.17,2:28:31.97,zimu,,0,0,0,,然后开始喝你的奶昔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}and starts to drink your milkshake.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.91,2:28:36.67,zimu,,0,0,0,,我在喝你的奶昔！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I drink your milkshake!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:38.88,2:28:42.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我把它喝光了！   - 丹尼尔，别逼我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I drink it up! - Don't bully me, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:45.09,2:28:50.29,zimu,,0,0,0,,就你那破嗓子和烂舞步，还有你   那点迷信就能无往不胜么，伊莱？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Did you think your song and dance and your superstition would help you, Eli?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.42,2:28:55.05,zimu,,0,0,0,,我才是第三启示！   我才是上帝选中的使者！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am the Third Revelation. I am who the Lord has chosen.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.26,2:28:59.56,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 丹尼尔！   - 因为我比你聪明！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- Daniel! - Because I'm smarter than you!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.67,2:29:01.13,zimu,,0,0,0,,我比你年长！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm older!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:01.97,2:29:03.80,zimu,,0,0,0,,我是你的老朋友呀，丹尼尔！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm your old friend, Daniel!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.90,2:29:06.34,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我可不是什么假先知…   - 救命！救命啊！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I'm not a false prophet... - Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:06.44,2:29:08.70,zimu,,0,0,0,,…你这乳臭未干的娃娃！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}...you sniveling boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:08.81,2:29:15.48,zimu,,0,0,0,,我就是第三启示！   我就是第三启示！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I am the Third Revelation! I am the Third Revelation!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:15.58,2:29:18.55,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我说过要生吃了你！   - 我们是亲人！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I told you I would eat you. - We're family!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:18.69,2:29:23.12,zimu,,0,0,0,,- 我说过要生吞了你！   - 我们是兄弟！是兄弟！\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}- I told you I would eat you up! - We're brothers! We're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.23,2:29:33.03,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔，请饶了我吧，求你了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Daniel, please forgive me. I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:36.70,2:29:38.76,zimu,,0,0,0,,在那儿，在那儿啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}That's it. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:41.17,2:30:42.64,zimu,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔先生？\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}Mr. Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.54,2:30:52.21,zimu,,0,0,0,,我没事了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs13}{\b0}I'm finished.
